ME (tnmedicalselection.net)</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Documents required for MD MS admissions</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>NEET PG 2023 Admit Card as well as Score card</li>\r\n	<li>MBBS degree and internship completion certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Medical registration (provisional or permanent) issued by MCI</li>\r\n	<li>Domicile Certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Caste certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Disability certificate (if applicable)</li>\r\n	<li>Payment receipt for the application form</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'mahatma-gandhi-medical-college-and-research-institute', '167644148959.jpg', '167644148952.jpg', 1, '2023-02-15', 'Application form for Counselling for MD MS admissions in Tamil Nadu:', 'Mahatma Gandhi Medical College and Research Institute (MGMCRI) is a leading medical institution in the country, having figured among the top 25 medical institutions, as per India Rankings 2018, released by NIRF, India.', NULL, '2023-02-15 12:11:29', '2023-02-15 15:36:48'),
(24, 'SRI LAKSHMINARAYAN COLLEGE OF PHARMACY', '<p>WELCOME TO SRI LAKSHMINARAYAN COLLEGE OF PHARMACY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences, Puducherry was born in the year 2006 with a vision to establish a multispecialty hospital where in particular poor could receive advanced care in an atmosphere of love and compassion. Annually 250 students admitted for undergraduate MBBS course, postgraduate degrees - Community Medicine, General Medicine, General Surgery and Radiology Otorhinolaryngology and Orthopaedics Dermatology Psychiatry Anaesthesiology Pediatrics Emergency Medicine Ophthalmology OBG Ph.D programmes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The application window for the NEET PG 2023 exam which is to be held on 5th March, 2023 is closed now but the Final Edit Window to rectify any uploaded image such as Photograph, Signature or Thumb impression will be open from 14th to 17th February, 2023.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Application form for Counselling for MD MS admissions in Tamil Nadu:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The counselling for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu is conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education, Tamil Nadu (DME). The application form for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu has not been released yet and will be available online at the official website <a href=\"https://tnmedicalselection.net/\">Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net)</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Post Graduate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/files/community-medicine.pdf\">M.D. (Preventive &amp; Social Medicine)/ Community Medicine</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (General Medicine)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.S. (General Surgery)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#%22\">M.D. (Radio-Diagnosis)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/files/ent.pdf\">M.S. (Otorhinolaryngology)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/files/orthopaedics.pdf\">M.S. (Orthopaedics)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (Dermatology., Venerology. &amp; Leprosy)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (Psychiatry)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.S. (Paediatrics)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (Anaesthesiology)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (Emergency Medicine)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.S. (Ophthalmology)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://slims.ac.in/courses.php#\">M.D. (Obstetrics &amp; Gynaecology)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Candidates who have been allotted through centralized counselling by the MCC of DGHS, New Delhi for admission to MBBS Degree courses in Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences,Puducherry for the academic year 2022-23, are advised to report and complete the admission process strictly within the date and time specified in the <strong>&lsquo;Allotment Letter&rsquo;</strong> issued by the <a href=\"http://www.mcc.nic.in/\"><strong>MCC - DGHS.</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS to the UG candidates allotted through centralized counselling by MCC of DGHS, New Delhi for admission to MBBS Courses (2022-23)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'sri-lakshminarayan-college-of-pharmacy', '167645699828.jpg', '167645699836.jpg', 1, '2023-02-15', 'SRI LAKSHMINARAYAN COLLEGE OF PHARMACY', 'The Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences, Puducherry was born in the year 2006 with a vision to establish a multispecialty hospital where in particular poor could receive advanced care in an atmosphere of love and compassion.', NULL, '2023-02-15 16:29:58', '2023-02-15 16:29:58'),
