OSTGRADUATE DIPLOMA COURSES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 year</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver51\">PG Diploma in Clinical Embryology</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'chettinad-medical-college', '167663322571.jpg', '1676633225100.jpg', 1, '2023-02-17', 'Chettinad Medical College', 'CARE is the first university of its kind in Chennai which has been conferred with Deemed University. The academic programs offered by CARE are job oriented, innovative and professional. We offer 74 Academic programs in the Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Allied Health Sciences(AHS), Pharmacy, Physiotherapy, Architecture, Commerce and Law. Most of the programs offered are recognized by MCI/NMC/TNNMC/COA/BCI/PCI and other regulators.', NULL, '2023-02-17 17:27:05', '2023-02-17 17:27:05');
