conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education (DME), Chennai, the dates of which shall be announced soon on the official website Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net).\">Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net)</a><a id=\"Tamil Nadu NEET PG Counselling 2023 is conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education (DME), Chennai, the dates of which shall be announced soon on the official website Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net).\" name=\"Tamil Nadu NEET PG Counselling 2023 is conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education (DME), Chennai, the dates of which shall be announced soon on the official website Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net).\">.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For state-wise online registration, visit<a id=\"www.nmc.org.in/information-desk/state-medical-councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/\" name=\"www.nmc.org.in/information-desk/state-medical-councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/\"> </a><a href=\"#www.nmc.org.in/information-desk/state-medical-councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/\">www.nmc.org.in/information-desk/state-medical-councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NEET PG Cut Off 2023 for <strong>MD/MS admissions in Tamil Nadu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General: 50th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General with physical disabilities: 45th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SC/ST/OBC: 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SC/ST/OBC with physical disabilities: 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'neet-pg-2023-participating-colleges-in-tamil-nadu', '', '', 1, '2023-03-21', 'NEET PG 2023 Participating Colleges in Tamil Nadu', 'Now that the result of NEET PG 2023 is out and the counselling for the same shall begin soon, it is advisable to be aware of all the colleges participating in the NEET PG 2023 Counselling to make an informed decision about MD/MS admissions in your preferred choice of institution.', NULL, '2023-03-21 12:14:59', '2023-03-21 12:14:59');
