(68, 'NEET PG 2023 Participating Colleges in Jharkhand and Bihar', '<p>For admission to various postgraduate medical programmes, such as MD/MS/Diploma in various government and private medical schools in India, the National Board of Examinations (NBE) conducts the NEET-PG (National Eligibility cum Entrance Test for Postgraduate). Now that the exam results have been revealed and the counselling for NEET PG 2023 will soon begin, it is essential to be aware of all the institutions participating in it in order to make an informed decision regarding <strong>MD/MS admissions 2023</strong> in your preferred choice of institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Application form for Counselling for <strong>MD/MS admissions </strong>in Jharkhand and Bihar</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The NEET PG Counselling for MD/MS admissions in Jharkhand is undertaken by the Jharkhand Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board (JCECEB). The application form for the same would be released in April, 2023 on the official website of <a href=\"https://jceceb.jharkhand.gov.in/\">https://jceceb.jharkhand.gov.in/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All applicants who seek to take admission in the state of Jharkhand under the 50% state quota must submit an application online to be eligible for NEET PG Counselling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For Bihar, Bihar Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board (BCECEB) conducts Bihar PG counselling for admission to various PG medical courses such as MD/MS/ PG Diploma courses. The application form for the same shall be available soon at <a href=\"https://bceceboard.bihar.gov.in/\">https://bceceboard.bihar.gov.in/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Private Medical Colleges of Jharkhand and Bihar for <strong>MD/MS admission</strong> based on NEET PG 2023 scores</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the best private medical colleges in Jharkhand and Bihar for <strong>MD/MS admissions</strong> include:<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:754px\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope=\"col