councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/\">www.nmc.org.in/information-desk/state-medical-councils/list-of-state-medical-councils/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>NEET PG Cut Off 2023 for <strong>MD/MS admissions in Tamil Nadu</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General:</strong> 50th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General with physical disabilities: </strong>45th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SC/ST/OBC:</strong> 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SC/ST/OBC with physical disabilities:</strong> 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'neet-pg-2023-participating-colleges-in-tamil-nadu', '', '168155519345.png', 1, '2023-04-15', 'NEET PG 2023 Participating Colleges in Tamil Nadu', 'Find the list of participating private colleges in Tamil Nadu for NEET PG 2023. Learn about the NEET PG cutoff for MD/MS admissions in Tamil Nadu. Apply now!', NULL, '2023-04-15 15:39:53', '2023-04-15 15:39:53');
