(87, 'Jahurul Islam Medical College', '<p>Jahurul Islam Medical College is a private medical college located in Bhagalpur, Bajitpur, Kishoreganj, Bangladesh. The college was established in 1992 and is affiliated with Dhaka University. Jahurul Islam Medical College offers undergraduate and postgraduate medical programs including MBBS, BDS and postgraduate degrees in various medical specialties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has a modern campus with state-of-the-art facilities including well-equipped classrooms, libraries, laboratories and a teaching hospital. The college also has a highly qualified and experienced faculty who are dedicated to providing quality education and training to their students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jahurul Islam Medical College is recognized by the Bangladesh Medical and Dental Council (BMDC) and is listed in the International Medical Education Directory (IMED). The college has also been approved by the Medical Council of India (MCI) to provide medical education to Indian students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBBS course details at Jahurul Islam Medical College:</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:602px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Course Duration</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>5 years</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Medium of Instruction</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>English</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Eligibility</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>70% marks in Physics, Chemistry, Biology in Class 12th.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>NEET Qualification</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Required</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>IELTS/TOEFL</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Not Required</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Type of University</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Private</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Intake</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>January</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Average Tuition Fee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Rs 48 lakhs for complete course (approx)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Official Website</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>http://jimedcol.org/</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility Criteria for MBBS admissions at Jahurul Islam Medical College:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Applicant must be at least 17 years of age</li>\r\n	<li>Qualifying NEET exam with at least 50 % marks is mandatory</li>\r\n	<li>Must score at least 70% marks in Class 12th from a recognized board.</li>\r\n	<li>Physics, Chemistry and Biology to be mandatory subjects in Class 12th.</li>\r\n	<li>English to be the medium of study for the qualifying examination.</li>\r\n	<li>Students with a break in studies of more than one year cannot apply for admissions at Jahurul Islam Medical College.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Process for MBBS Admissions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Submit the application form along with the required documents by post at the official address of the college:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Jahurul Islam Medical College &amp; Hospital</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delta Dahlia (9th Floor)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>36, Kemal Ataturk Avenue, Banani</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dhaka-1213, Bangladesh.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Admission to Jahurul Islam Medical College is done in accordance with the rules and regulations of&nbsp; Directorate General of Health Services (DGHS) and one is required to obtain an eligibility or Equivalence Certificate from DGHS for confirmation of admission at&nbsp; Jahurul Islam Medical College.</li>\r\n	<li>The selection of the candidate is on merit basis and the selected candidate will receive the offer letter from the college by email or post.</li>\r\n	<li>Pay the fees to confirm your seat.</li>\r\n	<li>Obtain a medical fitness certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Apply for Visa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Documents Required for MBBS Admissions at Jahurul Islam Medical College (JIMC)</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Admission/Invitation letter from JIMC</li>\r\n	<li>Mark sheets of Class 10th and 12th.</li>\r\n	<li>NEET Score card</li>\r\n	<li>Valid Passport</li>\r\n	<li>Medical certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Passport size photographs</li>\r\n	<li>HIV Negative Report</li>\r\n	<li>Covid Negative Report.</li>\r\n	<li>Equivalence Certificate from DGHS.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Food and Accommodation Facilities at Jahurul Islam Medical College (JIMC)</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Separate hostels are made available for both boys and girls by JIMC.</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel seats are allotted on a first come first serve basis and the students must reside in the room allotted to them.</li>\r\n	<li>Rooms are well furnished, homely and comfortable.</li>\r\n	<li>Other facilities in the hostel include common room for recreational activities, dining area, gymnasium etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Healthy, hygienic and tasty meal is served three times a day at the students&rsquo; common mess in the dining area.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Thus, JIMC is a complete MBBS destination for international students in terms of quality education, global recognition, comfortable living conditions as well as affordable fee structure.</p>', 'jahurul-islam-medical-college', '', '', 1, '2023-05-03', 'Jahurul Islam Medical College', 'Jahurul Islam Medical College is a private medical college located in Bhagalpur, Bajitpur, Kishoreganj, Bangladesh. The college was established in 1992 and is affiliated with Dhaka University. Jahurul Islam Medical College offers undergraduate and postgraduate medical programs including MBBS, BDS and postgraduate degrees in various medical specialties.', NULL, '2023-05-03 12:33:29', '2023-05-03 12:33:29');
