(1, 'Bhaarath Medical College & Hospital', 0, 'bhaarath-medical-college--hospital', 'Medical College', NULL, 31, 693, '164707806396.jpg', '163853555549.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'UGC, AIU Member, NAAC Accreditation (Grade \'A\')', '82 (2020)', '305 acre', '1500', '1984', '', '2500+', '<p>Bharath Institute of Higher Education and Research (BIHER) was established in Chennai, Tamil Nadu in 1984 by Sri Lakshmi Ammal Educational Trust, established by the academic visionary Dr. S.Jagathrakshakan. The institute is ranked 36th&nbsp;for University by NIRF in 2019. It has four institutions Sree Balaji College of Nursing, Chennai, Sree Balaji College of Physiotherapy, Chennai, Sree Balaji Medical College and Hospital (SBMCH), Chennai and Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences (SLIMS), Puducherry. It is recognised by the University Grants Commission (UGC) and also a Member of the Association of Indian Universities (AIU). It is also accredited with the Highest Grade &lsquo;A&rsquo; by NAAC, Government of India. It offers undergraduate and postgraduate programmes along with research-level programmes such as PhD in multiple fields such as Management, Engineering, Science and Humanities.</p>', 1, 'MBBS', 0, '{\"name\":\"Bhaarath Medical College & Hospital\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"streams\":\"Medical College\",\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2021-11-18 20:48:45', '2022-09-17 11:36:06'),
(6, 'A.C.S Medical College & Hospital', 0, 'acs-medical-college--hospital-2', '', 'india', 31, 693, '164636342167.jpg', '164636342180.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '6.8 acres', '450', '2008', '47.4', '2500+', '<p>The Faculty of Medical Sciences is an important department in the university and has a huge intake of students each year. The department comes fully equipped with a state-of-the-art laboratory, which makes it one of the best medical schools in Nigeria and other developing countries. The quality of education, infrastructural advantage and modern equipments are also some reasons why this university is very popular among students.</p>', 1, '', 0, '{\"name\":\"A.C.S Medical College & Hospital\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"BDS\\/MDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>Here are the ACS Medical College Facilities provided to the students who have confirmed their admission for ACS Medical College MBBS Courses:-</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Medical</td>\r\n			<td>Computer labs</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Library</td>\r\n			<td>Sports</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Auditorium</td>\r\n			<td>Cafeteria</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hostel</td>\r\n			<td>Laboratory</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hospital</td>\r\n			<td>O.P.D.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Centre for Community Medicine</td>\r\n			<td>Blood Bank</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Medical Social &amp; Welfare Services</td>\r\n			<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Undergraduate Program:-</h2>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:701px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff; vertical-align:top; width:307px\">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MBBS &ndash; Bachelor of Medicine Bachelor of Surgery</a></li>\r\n				<li>Postgraduate Program:-</li>\r\n				<l