(7, 'Sri Lalithambigai Medical College and Hospital', 0, 'sri-lalithambigai-medical-college-and-hospital', 'Medical College', NULL, 31, 693, '163844733437.png', '163844733497.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '37', '6.8 acres', '131+', '2008', '47.4', '50', '<p><strong>&ldquo;Sri&nbsp;</strong><strong>Lalithambigai</strong><strong>&nbsp;Medical College and Hospital&rdquo;</strong>&nbsp;which is started under the unit of&nbsp;<strong>Dr.M.G.R</strong><strong>&nbsp;Educational and Research Institute Deemed to be University</strong>. SLMCH is a class of its own, which is backed by advanced technologies and the latest equipment to serve people of all strata. We are assiduous to the achievement and maintenance of excellence in Education, Research, and Primary care for the welfare of mankind.</p>', 0, '', 0, '{\"name\":\"Sri Lalithambigai Medical College and Hospital\",\"degree\":null,\"streams\":\"Medical College\",\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\"}', NULL, '5', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-01 14:18:07', '2021-12-05 22:11:28'),
(8, 'Meenakshi Medical College Hospital And Research Institute', 0, 'meenakshi-medical-college-hospital-and-research-institute', 'MBBS', 'india', 31, 703, '163878257496.png', '163878257452.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '101', '39 Acres', '459', '2008', '1.24 Crores', '40', '<p>Meenakshi Medical College and Research Institute is one of the most forward-looking educational environments in medicine in the country. The college is dedicated to training doctors of various branches of medicine as experts in clinical skills and knowledge thereby applying it for the welfare of the community. The College and Hospital Complex has been raised in an area of 39.08acres, ideally located with salubrious surroundings. It is provided with state of art infrastructure in terms of its blocks of buildings, which include cosy, comfortable and well-furnished departments, laboratories etc.</p>', 1, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Meenakshi Medical College Hospital And Research Institute\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Kanchipuram\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\\/MD\\/MS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The college has a Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The central library has 22,000 of books 732 ebooks, subscribing for 81 International and 81 National journals and has 3133 back volumes. We are also subscribing for 1551 electronic journals. We follow the open access system. To make it user-friendly the library books are classified according to the library of Congress and National Library of Medicine classification and arranged them in the shelves by subject.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The college has sports facilities for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has an auditorium facility for events and seminar.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>The college has a transport facility for students and staff.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The college has a departmental based laboratories facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Banks Facilities\r\n	<p>The college has the Banks/ATM facilities for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The College and Hospital Complex has been raised in an area of 39.08acres, ideally located with salubrious surroundings. It is provided with state of art infrastructure in terms of its blocks of buildings, which include cozy, comfortable and well-furnished departments, laboratories, classrooms for students, separate quarters for staff and nurses besides equipment of latest technological quality. The institution is backed by highly qualified and experienced staff, well equipped laboratories, library and modern teaching aids.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>At present the hospital has 1,200 teaching beds with states of art operation theaters. Besides there are intensive care beds with 24 hours hi-tech trauma care facility, serving a wide cross section of community, belonging to every economic segment of society.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>The college has emerged as a pioneer in the state of Tamil Nadu by providing medical and health care programmes through internationalization, innovation in academic and research studies. The college offers under Graduates course in medicine (M.B.B.S.), postgraduate degree (M.D/M.S) in 19 medical disciplines and super specialty courses (M.Ch/DM) in 4 disciplines. The sanctioned annual intake to the M.B.B.S. programme is 250 students</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Learning Resources</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Sports</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>E-Journals&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ndash; 2821</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>E-Books&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &ndash; 439</p>\r\n\r\n	<h2>Laboratories</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>We provide state of the art laboratory facilities to its students, faculty and staff for carrying out teaching, research and practical activities.&nbsp; These laboratories provide practical exposure to multiple subjects and give an opportunity to the students to experiment with what they have learnt in classrooms.</p>\r\n\r\n	<h2>Library</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p><strong>Books</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>No of Titles&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &ndash; 9328</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>No of Volumes&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ndash; 20411</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>No of Textbooks&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ndash; 15822</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>No of Reference Books &ndash; 4589</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><strong>Journal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>National Journals (Print)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ndash; 67</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Foreign Journals (Print)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ndash; 53</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><strong>Online Resource (Subscribed)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>DELNET (Developing Library Network)</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>PROQUEST</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-01 14:39:14', '2023-02-20 14:48:15'),
(9, 'Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences', 0, 'sri-lakshmi-narayana-institute-of-medical-sciences', 'MBBS', NULL, 27, 588, '163878931614.png', '163878931677.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '', '360', '2006', '21.5 Lakhs', '140', '<p>Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences was born in the year 2006 with a vision to establish a multispecialty hospital in Agaram Village of Puducherry, Union Territory of India, wherein particular the poor could receive free advanced medical care in an atmosphere of love and compassion and to create a world-class teaching and research environment. Annually 150 students admitted for undergraduate MBBS degree course, postgraduate degrees in Eight specializations &ndash;Community Medicine, General Medicine, General Surgery, Radiology, Otorhinolaryngology, Orthopaedics, Dermatology, Psychiatry and PhD degree programmes. Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences recognized by Medical Council of India and Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare, Government of India, New Delhi and affiliated to Bharath Institute of Higher Education and Research, Chennai. The diversity of the College community makes for a stimulating and cosmopolitan atmosphere. About 30% of students are from other States and orientation programmes and English language support are provided.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'MBBS', 0, '{\"name\":\"Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Pondicherry\",\"city\":\"Pondicherry\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>These are the facilities that are provided to the students who have confirmed their admission or already studying from Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences Puducherry:-</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Medical</td>\r\n			<td>Computer labs</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Library</td>\r\n			<td>Sports</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Auditorium</td>\r\n			<td>Cafeteria</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hostel</td>\r\n			<td>Laboratory</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>HospO.P.D.l</td>\r\n			<td>O.P.D.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Centre for Community Medicine</td>\r\n			<td>Blood Bank</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '5', '', '<h3>Student Support</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Anti Ragging</li>\r\n	<li>Counselling Services</li>\r\n	<li>Healthcare Services</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel</li>\r\n	<li>Query</li>\r\n	<li>Report</li>\r\n	<li>Technical Issues</li>\r\n</ul>', '<h3><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>', '2021-12-06 16:00:00', '2022-03-04 07:58:17'),
(10, 'Vinayaka Missions Medical College And Hospital', 0, 'vinayaka-missions-medical-college-and-hospital', 'MBBS', NULL, 27, 586, '164707919262.jpg', '164631934343.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '101', '70 Acres', '91', '1996', '1,950,000', '702', '<p>One of the top private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is Vinayaka Mission&#39;s Sankarachariyar Dental College in Salem. The college was established in 1986&ndash;1987 and is commonly referred to as Vinayaka Mission Dental College Salem. The College has ties to Chennai&#39;s Tamil Nadu Dr. M.G.R. Medical University and has received government of India&#39;s Dental Council approval. The College was founded to strengthen the nation&#39;s weakest region, the rural population. Sankarachariyar Dental College Salem was established by Vinayaka Mission to provide students with the best oral and maxillofacial surgery as well as dental care.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vinayaka Missions Medical College is situated in the picturesque views of the Bay of Bengal. This institution was established in the year 1996 by our Former Chairman, (Late) Dr.A.Shanmugasundaram, a noble Philanthropist and Educationist of extraordinary vision in the field of education who is the founder of Vinayaka Missions University belonging to the Thirumuruga Kirupananda Variyar Thavathiru Sundara Swamigal Medical Educational &amp; Charitable Trust.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 2003, Vinayaka Missions Medical College and Hospital received permanent recognition from the Medical Council of India (MCI), Ministry of Health, Government of India. It was also renewed in the year 2010.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Faculty and Staff:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This college offers a solid mix of highly educated, well-trained, and technologically advanced faculty members. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for advancing and maintaining the standards of medical education at Vinayaka Mission Dental College Salem in their capacity as faculty members of the institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inappropriate variation in value-based approaches should be reduced</li>\r\n	<li>Give students more logical and sensible ways to approach the subject being taught.</li>\r\n	<li>Increasing attention to lifelong learning</li>\r\n	<li>To draw attention to the flaws in the material already available and suggest relevant future research</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The PDCH Pandur offers top-notch medical programmes with highly skilled faculty and cutting-edge facilities. For five years, the College has been renowned for its undergraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BDS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Duration: 4+1 years ( 4 years academics + 1 years internship )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission through TamilNadu NEET Counselling.</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:388px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:19px; vertical-align:bottom; width:172px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Category</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:19px; vertical-align:bottom; width:216px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Tuition fee per year</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:19px; vertical-align:bottom; width:172px\">\r\n			<p><strong>Management</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:19px; vertical-align:bottom; width:216px\">\r\n			<p>4,10,000</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />', 1, 'MBBS', 1, '{\"name\":\"Vinayaka Missions Medical College And Hospital\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"27\",\"city\":\"586\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>At Vinayaka Missions Medical College, Karaikal - Life in the campus is probably the most memorable period in the lives of the students. Multi-storied hostel buildings, built separately for men are equipped with all the amenities for comfortable living and with excellent mess facilities. The strict discipline which facilitates a conducive atmosphere for self-study is maintained to build the character of the students. Entertainment facilities are available for the hostellers to spend their leisure time. Internet facility is also made available in the men&rsquo;s hostel. Lush green atmosphere coupled with vast sports ground surrounds the hostel complexes.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>At Vinayaka Missions Medical College, Karaikal - Life in the campus is probably the most memorable period in the lives of the students. Multi-storied hostel buildings, built separately for women are equipped with all the amenities for comfortable living and with excellent mess facilities. The strict discipline which facilitates a conducive atmosphere for self-study is maintained to build the character of the students. Entertainment facilities are available for the hostellers to spend their leisure time. Internet facility is also made available in women&rsquo;s hostel. Lush green atmosphere coupled with vast sports ground surrounds the hostel complexes.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>Vinayaka Missions Medical College, Karaikal provides many indoor and outdoor games separately for boys and girls. Well equipped Gymnasiums with qualified trainers are available. Separate gym with modern equipment is made available in Gents and Ladies Hostel. Separate gym for faculty is also available in the staff quarters with all modern gymnasium equipments. Students enjoy and have an all-round development by participating and excelling in games. Annual Sports meet, Inter-Collegiate competitions and Sports programs are conducted every year at various campuses of our University giving the opportunity to improve the talent in games and keep the students physically fit. Vinayaka Missions Medical College, Karaikal has conducted two Inter- Collegiate Sports Tournaments in its campus and won the over-all-trophy twice.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The central library provides library services for any staff member. working College and hospital staff are encouraged to call, email or fax the VMMC librarian with any request. All requests are processed promptly. There are 14000 books. The following services are provided: Literature searches, Journal articles, Books, Current awareness services and Selective Dissemination of information (SD). Literature searches: Library service offers access to many specialized databases, including medicine, the Cochrane library, and CINAHL and can perform literature searches to find articles and information on a wide variety of topics. This is useful for finding research on any aspect of a specific disease or condition, finding the most up-to-date evidence-based information, finding information on current trends in health care, health policy health management and finding statistics collected by local, national &amp; worldwide health agencies.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>To conform to the adage &lsquo;sound mind in a sound body&rsquo;, a well equipped physical education department under on physical education director is functioning. There are outdoor facilities for football, volleyball, throw ball, cricket, and track. The students have won many laurels in various inter-college tournaments. Good teamwork and leadership development on the fields.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>Canteen facilities are available in both College and Hospital campuses of Vinayaka Missions Medical College. A separate hygienic central kitchen is available at our institution for preparation of food for the hostellers. Separate Kitchen facility is made available at all the hostels and quarters of our institution which are maintained under hygienic conditions. Delicious meals, refreshments, and snacks are available at reasonable rates.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has an auditorium facility for events and seminar.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>An intelligent mind is best ingrained in a healthy body. At Vinayaka Missions Medical College, health management is given due importance and is second only to intellectual and spiritual well-being. Health services provide general first-aid, emergency treatment, nutrition advice, eye, and ear testing and referral to specialist services. Vinayaka Health Club of our college provides guidance on health services. Simple and affordable insurance schemes are available for students to get health coverage. Medical services and consultations are free at our teaching Hospital and students are availing these facilities.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has an excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>Vinayaka Missions Medical College, Karaikal provide convenient transportation through a fleet of well-maintained buses that ply between the college and various locations at the towns. For the benefit of the students, the transportation charges are subsidized. Students are also permitted to come on their own vehicle. Wearing helmet is made compulsory for those who come on their own vehicle to the college. We have about fives buses and two mini buses for transportation of students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The following facilities are available to students who are considering attending or are already enrolled in the Vinayaka Mission&#39;s Sankarachariyar Dental College Salem: -</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Student Houses</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Clinical Facility</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Library</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Academic Facility</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Auditorium</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Laboratory</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 17:51:02', '2022-09-09 15:15:36'),
(11, 'Shri Sathya Sai Medical College and Research Institute', 0, 'shri-sathya-sai-medical-college-and-research-institute', 'MBBS', 'india', 31, 693, '167688726262.jpg', '167688726270.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '15,00,000 Sq.ft.', '150', '2008', '', '145', '<p>Shri Sathya Sai Medical College &amp; RI is located at Ammapettai, on Tiruporur Guduvancherry Main Road, 45 kms from Chennai Central Railway station, and 28 kms from the Chennai International Airport. It is well connected to the Chennai Metropolitan City by the Rajiv Gandhi Salai(OMR-IT corridor) which extends upto the famous Rock cave temple town of Mahabalipuram.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'MBBS', 0, '{\"name\":\"Shri Sathya Sai Medical College and Research Institute\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<h1>Eligibility criteria for NEET PG 2023:</h1>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Candidates who have completed MBBS and have the MBBS degree or provisional MBBS pass certificate recognized by the NMC</li>\r\n	<li>Candidates must possess a permanent or provisional registration certificate of MBBS qualification issued by the National Medical Commission (formerly known as Medical Council of India) or State Medical Council.</li>\r\n	<li>The applicant must have completed or likely to complete one year of Compulsory Rotating Resident Internship on or before 30th June, 2023. (The earlier cut-off date for completion of internship was 31st March, 2023 which has been extended to 30th June, 2023 now).</li>\r\n	<li>All Indian nationals can appear for NEET PG exam 2023</li>\r\n	<li>Foreign medical graduates (Indian citizens or OCIs) need to pass the Foreign Medical Graduate Examination (FMGE) to be eligible for the NEET PG exam and should also be registered by the NMC.</li>\r\n	<li>Foreign nationals should have completed MBBS or equivalent qualification as recognised by NMC and obtain a temporary registration issued by the NMC for the duration of the PG course.</li>\r\n	<li>There is no maximum age limit for the NEET PG exam.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additional eligibility criteria for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Candidates must possess an MBBS degree from a college recognised by the Dr. MGR Medical University or submit an eligibility certificate.</li>\r\n	<li>Domicile Certificate: Candidates must be domiciles of Tamil Nadu state to apply for PG admissions in the state and submit relevant supporting documents.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Application form for Counselling for MD MS admissions in Tamil Nadu:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The counselling for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu is conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education, Tamil Nadu (DME). The application form for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu has not been released yet and will be available online at the official website <a href=\"https://tnmedicalselection.net/\">Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net)</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>NEET PG Cut Off 2023 for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General: 50th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General with physical disabilities: 45th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SC/ST/OBC: 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SC/ST/OBC with physical disabilities: 40th percentile</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Documents required for MD MS admissions in Tamil Nadu:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>NEET PG 2023 Admit Card as well as Score card</li>\r\n	<li>MBBS degree and internship completion certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Medical registration (provisional or permanent) issued by MCI</li>\r\n	<li>Domicile Certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Caste certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Disability certificate (if applicable)</li>\r\n	<li>Payment receipt for the application form</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NRI candidates are required to submit a certificate stating the status of the candidate&rsquo;s financial supporter (local guardian) issued by the Indian Embassy of the respective country. A certificate stating the relationship of the local guardian with the applicant along with the passport and bank account details of the guardian must also be submitted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Counselling for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu 2023:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All candidates listed in the merit list declared by DME as per the NEET PG 2023 score will be eligible for PG counselling. The candidate must pay a non-refundable fee of Rs.1000 and select their preferred college as well as specialisation while filling the TN admissions application form.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Reservation Policy for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some seats are reserved for armed forces as well as under various state and management quota for PG admission in the government as well as private medical colleges of Tamil Nadu. 50% seats are reserved under state quota in various medical colleges of Tamil Nadu&nbsp; and the qualifying criteria for the same differs from one college to another. Kindly check the official website of the respective college for seat reservation guidelines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 18:03:32', '2023-02-20 16:04:15'),
(12, 'Sree Balaji Medical College And Hospital', 0, 'sree-balaji-medical-college-and-hospital', 'MBBS', NULL, 31, 693, '166368157026.png', '166368157036.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30.89 acres', '593', '1956', '2475000', '80', '<p><strong>Sree Balaji Medical College &amp; hospital</strong>&nbsp;has made rapid progress towards being recognized as a Medical school with high academic standards delivering quality health care with an emphasis on promoting social responsibility in its students. In keeping with the vision and mission of Bharath Institute of Higher Education and Research.Sree Balaji Medical College strives to generate competent and humane professionals empowered to face future challenges with ethical integrity.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSree Balaji Medical College &amp; Hospital is a constituent college of Bharath Institute of Higher Education and Research, Declared under section 3 of UGC Act, 1956. It is situated at Chromepet, Chennai. It is approved by Medical council of India , Ministry of Health and Family welfare, Govt of India, New Delhi. The college is situated in the heart of Chennai City and is close to the Chrompet Railway station, bus stand and Airport.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSree Balaji Medical College &amp; Hospital is a private, non profit, self financing medical Institution, pledged to the service of the community, catering to the healthcare needs of the people in general and especially to the needy, underprivileged, suffering section of humanity in particular.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe College and Hospital complex has been raised in an area of 30.89 acres, ideally located with salubrious surroundings. It is provided with state of art infrastructure in terms of its blocks of buildings, which include state of the art departments, laboratories, classrooms for students, separate quarters for staff and nurses besides equipment of the latest technological quality. Highly qualified and experienced staff, well-equipped laboratories, library, modern teaching aids and the hospital with huge patient flow, thus exposing students to various Medical and Surgical conditions are some highlights of the college.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe strive to offer the best of health care services to society and train students to develop into highly trained, knowledgeable, research-oriented and competent medical personalities and doctors.</p>', 0, 'MBBS', 1, '{\"name\":\"Sree Balaji Medical College And Hospital\",\"degree\":\"\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 18:16:44', '2022-09-20 18:46:10'),
(13, 'Chettinad Academy of Research and Education', 0, 'chettinad-academy-of-research-and-education-2', 'MBBS', NULL, 31, 695, '166368178147.jpg', '166368178180.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', 'CARE has been ranked 32nd among Medical colleges and ranked 15th among Private Medical Colleges by The Week 2020. NIRF has awarded CARE with the 98th rank among the best universities in India.', '30 Acres', '459', '2005', '2400000', '2500+', '<p>Chettinad Academy of Research and Education has about 2500+ students studying UG, PG and PhD education. University also proffers 100% scholarship to the students. Chettinad Academy of Research and Education has established an instrumentation facility as well for biomedical research and a CPCSEA approved animal house facility for translational research for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chettinad Academy of Research and Education offers quality research opportunities to the students of phD, hence providing JRF. Chettinad Academy of Research and Education has 1100 + research publications, has 35 patent publications and 50+ active MoUs with best academic institutions like Linkoping University, Sweden, Italy besides MOUs with industries, ReGenera Research Group for Aging Intervention &amp; Milano Medical Health Aging Unit. Adding to this, CARE too received funding from DST, DST Indo-Italy, DST-ECR, DBT, CSIR, ICMR, RSSDI etc., for research projects in all emerging areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Fusion Chettinad&rdquo;, is an annual event organised by the students every year that has participation from all over Tamil Nadu. Internal e-Newsletter &ldquo;CARE KONNECT &#39;&#39; is to keep the students to keep them updated about the activities about the college. Chettinad Academy of Research and Education offers decent infrastructure to students that includes 2 auditoriums with 1200 and 500 seating capacity. Wi-Fi enabled campus houses Hospital, academic and administrative blocks, separate hostels for girls, boys and apartments and villas for staff and faculty. Chettinad Academy of Research and Education campus also offers Bank, ATMs, food courts, stationary shop, and gymnasium and beauty parlour</p>', 0, 'MBBS', 1, '{\"name\":\"Chettinad Academy of Research and Education\",\"degree\":\"\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"695\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 19:04:44', '2022-09-20 18:49:41'),
(14, 'Tagore Medical College & Hospital', 0, 'tagore-medical-college--hospital', 'MBBS', NULL, 31, 693, '166340017765.jpg', '166340017725.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30 Acres', '220', '2007', '3,40,000', '2500+', '<p>The Tagore Educational Trust developed and oversees Tagore Dental College &amp; Hospital in Chennai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The government&#39;s Ministry of Health and Family Welfare has approved the dental college. of India and the Indian Dental Council (DCI).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Dr. MGR Medical University in Tamilnadu is linked with the Institute.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college strives to provide high-quality education that will foster technical and professional competence while also moulding the character and personality of its students with enough knowledge to prepare them for the challenges of the outside world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Founded in 2007; Affiliated with Dr. MGR Medical University</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289850\"></a><a name=\"_Hlk113289350\"><strong>Courses Offered</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>High-caliber medical programmes are provided by Tagore Dental College and Hospital Chennai under the direction of highly competent faculty and cutting-edge facilities. The College is renowned for its five-year undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289118\"><strong>BDS</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Duration:&nbsp;<strong>4+1 years ( 4 years academics + 1 years internship )</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission through TamilNadu NEET Counselling.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fees&nbsp;for&nbsp;courses&nbsp;(Annual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; 3,40,000/-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 'MBBS', 1, '{\"name\":\"Tagore Medical College & Hospital\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p><strong>Facilities.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following amenities provided by Tagore dental college and hospital are</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a name=\"_Hlk113288885\">Medical</a></li>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Sport</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 19:37:12', '2022-09-17 12:36:17'),
(15, 'Indira Medical College and Hospital', 0, 'indira-medical-college-and-hospital', 'MBBS', NULL, 31, 693, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '101', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'MBBS', 0, '{\"name\":\"Indira Medical College and Hospital\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\"}', NULL, '5', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-06 19:45:06', '2021-12-06 19:45:06'),
(16, 'Madha Medical College & Research Institute', 0, 'madha-medical-college--research-institute', 'MBBS', NULL, 31, 693, '166341469644.jpg', '166341469644.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '6.8 Acres', '150', '2011', '1600000', '308', '<p>Madha Hospital with its multi-specialty units and a team of highly dedicated and committed doctors in different area of expertise renders remarakable service at Thandalam, Near Kovoor. The entire team reaches the people in and around the area towards creating awareness on health and hyglenic way of living. Also they have conducted several camps for the people nearby village with the aid of the Founder and Chairman of Loorhu Ammal Trust. Under the aegis of the Founder and Chairman, the Madha Hospital provides free treatment and medication for the poor people. In order to facilitate the people, hospital is operated 24/7 with its full-fledged facility and trained nurses along with a team of doctors. The Madha hospital is attached with all sorts of facility namely X-ray unit, Scan Centre, Diagnosis lab etc which enables the people to avail all facility under one roof.</p>', 0, 'MBBS', 0, '{\"name\":\"Madha Medical College & Research Institute\",\"degree\":\"\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-06 19:54:05', '2022-09-17 16:38:16'),
(42, 'SUBHARTI DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'subharti-dental-college', '', NULL, 33, 802, '164706682031.png', '164706682035.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Constituent', '', '200 acres', '137', '1996', '', '', '<p>Welcome to Subharti Dental College, Meerut, a centre of education, research &amp; highest level of clinical care. Here we cultivate in our students the values of shiksha (education) sewa (service) &amp; sanskar (human values) Affiliated to Swami Vivekanand Subharti University, this college offers a variety of courses; Bachelor of Dental Surgery (BDS), Master of Dental Surgery (MDS), Diploma in Dental Machanic (DDM) &amp; PhD in Dental Sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Subharti Dental College was started under the umbrella of Subharti KK B Charitable Trust in the year 1996. &ldquo;Subharti&rdquo; is a manifestation of the ideas of Dr. Atul Krishna a noted surgeon of western Uttar Pradesh &amp; Dr. Mukti Bhatnagar a reputed physician &amp; medical imaging specialist.he idea of Subharti was born in the mind of Dr Atul Krishna when he was a young medical student of LLRM Medical College Meerut in 1974 as social service organization.In 1995 Subharti K K B Charitable Trust was established to give practical shape to dreams &amp; aspirations of the team at Subhartipuram. The dental college was the first educational project of this dynamic group and it started functioning initially on the premises of Lokpriya Hospital, a privately owned and hugely popular general hospital in Meerut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new campus was meanwhile taking shape on Delhi-Haridwar Bypass Road and the college was shifted here in 1999. Several other colleges came up on its premises including Subharti Medical College, Nursing and Physiotherapy colleges, an engineering and law college etc. In 2008, the Subharti group of institutions was finally awarded the status of a private University which is now a approx 200 acre educational township on the outskirts of Meerut city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The university has been named the Swami Vivekanand Subharti University in respect and memory of that great Indian monk and teacher.</p>', 0, '', 0, '{\"name\":\"SUBHARTI DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Meerut\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<h2>Infrastructure</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>CAFETERIAS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Three cafeterias with a wide variety of hot and cold foods are open seven days a week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LIBRARY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-equipped with huge volumes of books and various national and international journals are available for the students which is functional from 8:00 am to 11:00 pm.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Total Number of books:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6476</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Books - No. of titles:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1657</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Current subscription to Journals:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>53</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Indian Journals:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>14</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>International Journals:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>39</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Thesis</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>271</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>CD ROMs + DVDs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>184</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Facilities in the Library</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Photocopying facility</li>\r\n	<li>Internet facility</li>\r\n	<li>Online journals</li>\r\n	<li>Question bank</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This centrally located and easily accessible is perhaps the most happening place for the students of college.. As one enters this well lit, fire alarm fitted, esthetically designed and executed library, one gets into an atmosphere for serious intellectual work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any member of this University has free access to a rich collection of more than 29000 books, around 450 journals, 3528 thesis and more than 45000 back issues at any time between 8 a.m. to 10 p.m. on working days and 8 a.m. to 8 p.m. on holidays. To make it user friendly, books are classified under &ldquo;Dewey Decimal Classification&rdquo;. All departments have a separate departmental library with the respective specialty books and journals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LECTURE HALLS AND AUDITORIUMS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A lecture hall is situated on each floor of the dental college. In total there are four lecture halls. The lecture halls are provided with modern gadgets such as LCD projectors, multimedia systems and slide projectors. There is an air-conditioned lecture hall with a seating capacity of over 200 with modern facilities. The university has two huge auditoriums where cultural events, annual days, meetings, inter-college events are held.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DENTAL MUSEUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has a dental museum located on the second floor of the college building. In teaching dental subjects, the role of museums is exceptionally vital. The specimens of skull and teeth give direct knowledge to students. The different specimens, and the educational models well arranged in the museum instil habit of observation and research. The different specimens made available in the museum of this college make the teaching enjoyable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HOSTELS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college is equipped with separate hostel facilities within the campus for both boys and girls. Recreational facilities including gymnasium are also provided.</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-10 05:26:39', '2022-03-12 13:08:43'),
