(44, 'ISF COLLEGE OF PHARMACY', NULL, 'isf-college-of-pharmacy', 'MBBS', NULL, 28, 605, '164706189020.png', '164706189011.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'NAAC , AICTE, UGC, PCI, NIRF', 'Ranked 67 for University by NIRF 2021', '5 ACRES', '85', '1984', '', '972', '<p>37 Years of Excellence in Pharma Education &amp; Research&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Global Approach : Students from 10 Different Countries&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diversity : Student from 18 States&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Great Intellectual Pool: 70+ Faculty from 17 States to Nurture Building Pharmacists</p>\r\n\r\n<p>100+ GPAT Qualified Students&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RANKED IN PHARMACY :22nd</p>', 1, 'MBBS', 1, '{\"name\":\"ISF COLLEGE OF PHARMACY\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Punjab\",\"city\":\"Moga\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>The Institutional campus is spread on an area of 6.5 acres land and possess pollution free and lush green scenic environment. The institute is fully automated and centrally designed intellect faculty pool in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ANIMAL HOUSE&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MEDICINAL GARDEN&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SPECIALIZED LABS&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMART ORATION CENTERS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DR. RADHAKRISHNAN KNOWLEDGE CENTER</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>ISF Hostel is &ldquo;a home away from home&rdquo;. The Institute has magnificently designed separate hostels for boys with all modern facilities, for boarding and other recreational activities. The hostels have their own mess to provide good and hygienic food to the students. Room Categories150 bedded hostels consist of an air-conditioned single, double and triple room with modern furniture. All rooms have attached washrooms. AC rooms with single occupancy rooms with shared occupancyNormal rooms with single occupancyNormal rooms with shared occupancy.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Girls Hostel</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>ISF Hostel is &ldquo;a home away from home&rdquo;. The Institute has magnificently designed separate hostels for girls with all modern facilities, for boarding and other recreational activities. The hostels have their own mess to provide good and hygienic food to the students. Room Categories 150 bedded hostels consist of an air-conditioned single, double and triple room with modern furniture. All rooms have attached washrooms. AC rooms with single occupancy rooms with shared occupancyNormal rooms with single occupancyNormal rooms with shared occupancy.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Gym<br />\r\n	Keeping in mind the health and fitness of its students and staff, the College provides a state-of-the-art gymnasium, fully-equipped with the latest equipment within the campus. Instructor or trainer is also available to train the students and staff. The membership to the gymnasium can be availed by all the students and faculty. One can utilize this &lsquo;Fun-N-Fit Zone&rsquo; either in the morning or in the evening as per the convenience.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Library<br />\r\n	ISFCP has its own library named the Dr. Radhakrishanan Knowledge Resource Centre. The library has four different study rooms viz. Periodical Section, Stack Room, two Reading rooms and one Lobby. Every room centrally air-conditioned, well-ventilated and peaceful. ISFCP library has more than 16300 books, 20 newspapers including English, Hindi, and Punjabi. The college has a subscription of 100 international and 50 national journals and all the books are managed through Libsys system. The thesis of every pass out student is available in the library and there are total 587 theses including the Ph.D. and M.Pharm; always accessible for reference purposes. Reference books include British Pharmacopoeia, Indian Pharmacopoeia, European Pharmacopoeia, and the United States Pharmacopoeia. For the news and current updates, there is an LCD present in the Lobby. Centrally Air-conditionedXerox, LAN, Wi-Fi Networking system and LCD facilityInternational E-journalsModern Software (Libsys)Reading room for M.Pharm and Research students working hours of the library are from 9:30 am to 8:00 pm.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Sports<br />\r\n	With a view to developing the all-round personality of the students, the college emphasizes as much on sports as on academics. The College encourages students to attain sporting excellence and provides all the necessary facilities and equipment to the students for maintaining physical fitness and good health. The college offers an extensive range of sports and fitness classes throughout the academic session. Qualified staff and trainers deliver programmes for all ages, tastes and abilities, from Cricket to Yoga to Weight Training and Aerobics. There are training facilities for all the games, which groom the students and train them rigorously to compete at the national level. The infrastructure has been designed with good facilities for sports as well as recreational activities. The College has top sports facilities including the following: Cricket GroundFootball GroundsBasket Ball CourtsBadminton CourtsVolleyball CourtsFacility for Aerobics and DanceGrass PitchesIndoor Strengthening and Weight Training Gymnasium.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Cafeteria<br />\r\n	The College campus offers an excellent choice of places to eat. The College offers Food Court and ISFCP Canteen which offer delicious food, superior services with care. The eating joints offer excellent multi-cuisine menus ranging from Indian to Continental and Chinese in a comfortable and vibrant ambiance. A wide variety of fresh juices, cold coffee, milkshakes, and other beverages are also available. Apart from providing college Food court and Canteen, there is Caf&eacute; Coffee Day having an enormous range of recipes from coffee and other eating stuff like sandwiches, snacks, fresh fruits, cakes etc. in front of the campus. Famous food joints like Dominos, Subway, Baskin Robbins, Havmore, Chocolate Room, LC etc. are also providing services at Moga.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Auditorium<br />\r\n	Considering that a variety of events like conferences, seminars, cultural programmes, debates, plays and other programmes are conducted throughout the year, the college houses an auditorium and numerous other performing areas, which facilitate the students to carry out their activities in the right environment, smoothly and with ease. The Auditorium, Shri BaldevKrishanMemorial Auditorium, is centrally air-conditioned with a fully soundproof setup and equipped with the latest technology for all types of audio/video presentations. A number of small digital oration centers are also available for seminars, meetings, orientations, interactions, grooming sessions, workshops etc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Medical/Hospital<br />\r\n	The College have acute health care services with first aid facilities with over 60 pharmacist staff and well-renowned Physician. We have excellent medical support and round the clock medical facility for students in collaboration with leading hospitals of Moga and surrounding regions. Hostel wardens accompany students in case of any medical emergency to the best of the doctors in town. Homely care and timely treatment are assured through personal attention.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Wifi<br />\r\n	Computers with internet and WiFi facility with 10 Mbps capacity.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>IT Infrastructure<br />\r\n	Providing a sufficient number of LCD projectors for interactive learning. Providing a sufficient number of CD material with interactive learning in the library. Computers with internet and WiFi facility with 10 Mbps capacity.Provision of interactive learning and assessment modules as CD &amp; PPTs.Use of simulation software&rsquo;s for animal experimentations during lab hours. Use of open educational resources available online.Use of Multimedia for effective course delivery. Teaching with web linked material. Use of simulations for demonstrations of animal experiments.Use of e-journal, e-books for effective teaching.Use of software as computational or statistical tools.Use of webinars for effective teaching.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Transport<br />\r\n	Transport facility is allotted an annual basis for students for the duration of the academic session. Transport facility will be allotted on First Come First Serve basis. Routes and pick up points are indicative and are subject to change from time to time. Routine timings for College Bus to arrive at the College Campus will be 9:00 a.m. and departure at 5:00 p.m unless otherwise announced by the College.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Laboratories<br />\r\n	The college has a departmental based laboratories&nbsp;facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2021-12-20 15:05:41', '2022-03-12 12:09:27'),
(45, 'Santosh Medical Colleges and Hospitals', NULL, '-santosh-medical-colleges-and-hospitals-2', 'MBBS', NULL, 33, 749, '164276292995.jpg', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '', '', '1995', '24,00,000', '140', '<p>In 1995, the Santosh Medical/Dental Colleges and Hospitals came up as one of the top institutions in India to study medicine in Ghaziabad. The university has been offering an MBBS course since 1996 with a total intake of around 50 students per year. 2005 onwards, the course was recognised by the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare of the Government of India and the capacity of accepting a particular number of admissions was increased to 100. 20 years after its inception, the institute is considered as the best medical university, India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the same manner, Santosh Dental College started in 1995 with an aim of imparting a higher-level education in dentistry. The institution offers a foundation course in BDS since 1996 by accepting about 40 students annually. But the number of admissions went up higher to 100 per year after 2005. It has now become the best university for higher education.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Santosh Medical Colleges and Hospitals\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Agra\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '', '5.0', '', NULL, NULL, '2021-12-20 15:52:59', '2022-01-21 17:02:09'),
(46, 'Santosh Medical Colleges and Hospitals', NULL, '-santosh-medical-colleges-and-hospitals-2', 'MBBS', NULL, 33, 777, '163999599828.jpg', '163999599865.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Constituent', '101', '', '105', '1995', '24,00,000', '621', '<p>In 1995, the Santosh Medical/Dental Colleges and Hospitals came up as one of the top institutions in India to study medicine in Ghaziabad. The university has been offering an MBBS course since 1996 with a total intake of around 50 students per year. 2005 onwards, the course was recognised by the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare of the Government of India and the capacity of accepting a particular number of admissions was increased to 100. 20 years after its inception, the institute is considered as the best medical university, India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the same manner, Santosh Dental College started in 1995 with an aim of imparting a higher-level education in dentistry. The institution offers a foundation course in BDS since 1996 by accepting about 40 students annually. But the number of admissions went up higher to 100 per year after 2005. It has now become the best university for higher education.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Santosh Medical Colleges and Hospitals\",\"streams\":\"MBBS\",\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Ghaziabad\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p><strong>Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad&nbsp;</strong>provides certain facilities to the students and faculty members of the institute including sports, library, laboratories, hostels, gymnasium, laboratories, hospital etc. Detailed description of all the facilities provided to the students and faculty members of the institute are mentioned below.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Sports facilities-</strong>&nbsp;Various sports facilities are provided by Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad for the students. Various playgrounds for playing cricket, volleyball, kho-kho, kabaddi, track and field events. Other indoor games facilities like carrom, chess, badminton etc are also provided by the Institute.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Library-</strong>&nbsp;The central library of Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad is well equipped with a good collection of books, journals (National &amp; International), CDs to provide all necessary information to the students and faculty members of the institute. The library also has a reading room section where students and other visitors can read and refer to books. Other facilities like reprography and book lending are also available.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Laboratories-</strong>&nbsp;Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad has provided labs for different subjects for conducting practical experiments and students to do their project works. All the labs are well organised and equipped with necessary equipment. Lab technicians are also there to guide and help students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Hostels-</strong>&nbsp;Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad provides separate hostels to boys and girls. Students have to fill the application forms for hostels separately and rooms are allotted based on the availability. All the hostel rooms are provided with basic furniture and facilities. Mess facilities are also available for hostellers which serves good quality and hygienic food to students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Gymnasium-&nbsp;</strong>Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad provides gymnasium facilities for the students, faculty and staff all throughout the day. The gym is fully air-conditioned and well equipped with all necessary equipment needed for conducting all exercises and workouts. Trainers are also provided to guide and help students and faculty during their workout sessions.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Laboratories-</strong>&nbsp;Santosh Medical College, Ghaziabad has provided labs for different subjects for conducting practical experiments. All the labs are well organised and equipped with necessary equipment. Lab technicians are also there to guide and help students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Hospital-&nbsp;</strong>Santosh Medical Hospital was established in 2015 with 645 beds providing all medical facilities and treatment to patients. The hospital has several departments including Pediatrics, Gynecology &amp; Obstetrics, General Surgery, Ophthalmology, Pulmonary Medicine, Dental, Occupational Therapy, Orthopedic, General Medicine, ENT, Skin &amp; VD, Psychiatry, Physiotherapy etc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The college has a Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a library facility for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The college has sports facilities for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has auditorium facility for the seminar.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi\r\n	<p>The college has Wi-Fi facility for the students and staff.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>The college has a transport facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratories\r\n	<p>The college has departmental based laboratories facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Alumni Associations\r\n	<p>The college has good networking for the alumni association.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-20 16:00:15', '2021-12-20 16:26:38'),
