(48, 'Rural Medical College', NULL, 'rural-medical-college', '', NULL, 21, 496, '164276226872.jpg', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Constituent', '', '120 Acres', '445', '1984', '14,50,000', '1155', '<p>Rural Medical College, Loni was established in the year 1984 for healthcare, research and to provide socially meaningful medical education. The college is spread over 120 acres of land. &nbsp;Earlier, the institute was affiliated to Maharashtra University of Health Sciences, Nashik and the University of Pune and later on it got affiliated to Pravara Institute of Medical Sciences &ndash; Deemed to be University. Rural Medical College, Loni is recognised by the Medical Council of India and General Medical Council, U.K. The institute offers undergraduate and postgraduate courses to the students.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Rural Medical College\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Maharashtra\",\"city\":\"Latur\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>Rural Medical College, Loni has adequate infrastructure like a library which helps the students to have a hassle-free learning experience throughout their college life. It also provides facilities to the students like canteen, sports, etc in order to give them a break from the regular academic schedule they follow. Students can avail these facilities in their free time for their recreation.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Library:&nbsp;</strong>The institution has a library that has all kinds of text and reference books for the students and is a perfect place for book lovers.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Laboratories:</strong>&nbsp;The institution has laboratories for the students in order to apply their knowledge practically and gain exposure. These laboratories are well equipped with the latest technologies and equipment.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Sports:&nbsp;</strong>The institute provides sports facilities and encourages them to participate in indoor and outdoor games for their physical and mental well being.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Hostel:</strong>&nbsp;The institution provides hostel facilities to boys and girls. Students can avail the facilities of Wi-Fi networks, indoor games, TV rooms, etc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Canteen:</strong>&nbsp;The institution has a canteen that provides hygienic food to the students at a subsidised rate.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Auditorium:</strong>&nbsp;Rural Medical College, Loni has an auditorium with a seating capacity of 1200 students which is used in organising events and activities for the students.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Medical Facilities:</strong>&nbsp;In order to cater to the medical needs of the students the institution provides medical facilities to the students, staff and faculty.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', NULL, NULL, '2021-12-28 17:23:39', '2022-01-21 16:51:08'),
(49, 'Bharati Vidyapeeth University Medical College, Pune', NULL, 'bharati-vidyapeeth-university-medical-college-pune', '', 'india', 21, 507, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'UGC', '', '25 acres', '300', '1989', '19,35,515', '1600', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bharati Vidyapeeth (Deemed to be University) Medical College, Pune was established in February 1989 and is renowned for its academic excellence and infrastructural facilities. It was initially affiliated to the University of Pune till it became a constituent unit of Bharati Vidyapeeth (Deemed to be University) in April 1996.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Bharati Vidyapeeth University Medical College, Pune\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Maharashtra\",\"city\":\"Pune\",\"degree\":\"MBBS,MD\\/MS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2022-01-05 19:24:44', '2023-02-27 16:57:18'),
(50, 'Aarupadai Veedu Medical College and Hospital (AVMC)', NULL, 'aarupadai-veedu-medical-college-and-hospital-avmc', '', NULL, 31, 725, '164387217539.jpg', '164387217525.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Constituent', '', '25 acres', '184', '2000', '19,50,000', '800', '<p>Thirumuruga Kirupananda Variyar Thavathiru Sundara Swamigal Medical Educational and Charitable Trust were started by our Founder Chancellor Dr. A. Shanmugasundaram in the year 1981 to serve the needy in the society. The Trust established the very first medical college in Pondicherry, Aarupadai Veedu Medical College and Hospital in the year 2000. Located in NH Pondicherry - Cuddalore Road, a national highway, the self-contained and serene campus is spread over 44 acres of lush green lands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Initially the Institution was affiliated to Pondicherry University subsequently it came under the ambit of Vinayaka Mission&#39;s Research Foundation Deemed to be University, in the year 2004. The Institution offers Post Graduate courses in 13 disciplines and Ph.D. programs across various specialities and interdisciplinary areas. The first batches of 100 students were admitted for 2000-2001 sessions, and every year thereafter. At present, the annual intake is 150 MBBS and 74 Post Graduate students, and over 750 UG and POSTGRADUATE Students are pursuing their studies at AVMCH.</p>', 1, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Aarupadai Veedu Medical College and Hospital (AVMC)\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"725\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2022-01-14 17:10:15', '2022-09-17 14:10:19'),
(51, 'GS Medical College and Hospital, Hapur', NULL, 'gs-medical-college-and-hospital-hapur', '', NULL, 33, 776, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"GS Medical College and Hospital, Hapur\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Gautam Buddha Nagar\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '', '', '', '', '2022-01-29 17:24:19', '2022-01-29 19:38:41'),
(52, 'Heritage Institute of Medical Sciences', NULL, 'heritage-institute-of-medical-sciences', '', NULL, 33, 821, '164346979251.jpg', '164346979287.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Government (Affiliated)', '', '12 lac square feet', '220', '2015', '7006914', '1778', '<p>Heritage Institute of Medical Sciences, a pioneering institution committed to delivering the best of healthcare, education and medical experiences in Purvanchal. Approved by Government of India and National Medical Commission (NMC) , HIMS is a medical institute with a built up area of more than 12 lac square feet, and an accomplished faculty to prepare the best doctors of coming times.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Heritage Institute of Medical Sciences\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Varanasi\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lecture Theaters:&nbsp;Four fully air-conditioned lecture theatres, gallery type with 180/200 seating capacity complete with audiovisual aids and facility for E-conferencing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Demo Rooms:&nbsp;All the<strong>&nbsp;</strong>preclinical and paraclinical departments have been provided with two demo rooms each with 80-90 seating capacity and audiovisual aids.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Common Rooms:&nbsp;Separate well-furnished common rooms for boys and girls with attached toilets having 100 seating capacity each have been provided in the college block.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4) &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Labs:&nbsp;Well furnished and well equipped<strong>&nbsp;</strong>Lab with a seating capacity of 90 each with attached anterooms have been provided for conducting practical classes as per NMC norms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Library:&nbsp;Fully air-conditioned central library with a carpet area of more than 28000 sq. ft. has been provided in the college block. The library has the&nbsp;facility of an outside reading room for 150 students as well as an inside reading room for the students and the staff. Internet facility with 20 nodes each has been provided for the students and the staff. The library has a requisite number of the latest medical books on different subjects as well as National and International scientific journals. The library is open for use of students and the staff from 8.00 AM to 8.00 PM on all working days and 9.00 Am to 5.00 PM on Sundays&nbsp;and holidays.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Auditorium&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7) Cafeteria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8) Gymnasium&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9) Doctors resident&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10) Hostels&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11) Mess&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12) Computer Lab&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13) Skill Lab&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14) Recreation Facilities</p>', '4.3', '', '', '', '2022-01-29 20:22:02', '2022-01-29 21:23:12'),
(53, 'Hind Institute of Medical Sciences', NULL, 'hind-institute-of-medical-sciences', '', NULL, 33, 761, '164362137747.jpg', '164362137746.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '305', '2009', '1170612', '1586', '<p><strong>Hind Institute of Medical Sciences (HIMS), Lucknow&nbsp;</strong>was established in the year 2009 and it is recognised by the Medical Council of India (MCI), Indian Nursing Council and Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare, Government of India. HIMS Lucknow offers a total of 35 courses at the diploma, undergraduate and postgraduate levels. The institute is affiliated to&nbsp;Dr. Ram Manohar Lohia Avadh University, Faizabad. HIMS Lucknow has a total student enrollment of 1586 and a faculty size of 305 members. The institution offers admission in the streams of medicine &amp; allied sciences, pharmacy and sciences. HIMS Lucknow provides a variety of facilities and infrastructure to its students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The mission of the institute is to provide the best teaching of medical, paramedical courses with modern infrastructure and facilities. The vision of the institute is to provide free medical care to the weaker sections of society.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Hind Institute of Medical Sciences\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Barabanki\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li>Central Library</li>\r\n		<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n		<li>Lecture Theatres</li>\r\n		<li>Gymnasium</li>\r\n		<li>Canteen</li>\r\n		<li>Blood Bank &amp; Component</li>\r\n		<li>Museums</li>\r\n		<li>CSSD &amp; Laundry</li>\r\n		<li>Ayushman Bharat</li>\r\n		<li>Jan Aaushadhi Kendra</li>\r\n		<li>HDFC Bank</li>\r\n		<li>Prayer Room</li>\r\n		<li>Central Research Lab</li>\r\n		<li>Residences &amp; Hostels</li>\r\n		<li>Diagnostics</li>\r\n		<li>Games- Indoor &amp; Outdoor</li>\r\n		<li>Delhi World Public School</li>\r\n		<li>Pharmacy</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '', '', 