(54, 'SUBHARTI MEDICAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'subharti-medical-college-', '', NULL, 33, 802, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SUBHARTI MEDICAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Meerut\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-03-03 15:10:39', '2022-03-03 15:10:39'),
(55, 'GAUTAM INSTITUTE OF PHARMACY', NULL, 'gautam-institute-of-pharmacy', '', NULL, 5, 167, '164691079956.png', '164691079960.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '2008', '', '', '<h2>About us</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Right Path Foundation is a registered charitable trust dedicated to work for professional/technical capacity building and skill development education &amp; training for youths to help in building their career and generate or enhance jobs/earning opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gautam Group of Institutions has owned the responsibility for educating and providing teaching skills to youths who are ready to enter teaching career and provide vital career developing education to our future generation. We wish to become the best teacher training college in the region through the teaching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>One of the major objectives of Right Path Foundation is &ndash;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&#39;To open, establish, promote, set-up, maintain, support and/or help literacy, informal, formal and/or distance education programmes/activities including technical/non-technical, professional, management, teacher&rsquo;s training, art &amp; craft, vocational and physical education/training/course by any or all types of schools, colleges, universities, training/coaching centres, hostels, research or other institutions of the like nature for the purpose.&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Establishment &amp; Management of educational and training institutions for providing opportunities to youths to develop professional and technical skills in different sectors is one of the major objectives of the Foundation. It is a proven fact that a healthy mind resides in a healthy body. Good health, be it of mind or body, is vital for a good quality of life. Helping someone else in building or maintaining a healthy quality of life is all the more important and satisfying community service. Requirements for technically skilled personnel dedicated to health care services are immense. So, it is important to join hands in at least filling the gap of trained manpower in health service sector. Mata Sushila Institute of Education is committed to impart the best quality of education &amp; training in nursing skills/techniques.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"GAUTAM INSTITUTE OF PHARMACY\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Bihar\",\"city\":\"Nalanda\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>OUR CAMPUS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wide range explored infrastructure with all the required norms. Upgraded Laboratories with highly sophisticated techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ADMINISTRATION</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are with top management &amp; professionals as per the courses we offer. Professionals along with experienced professors deals with the related Courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FACULTY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Faculty of the institute possess outstanding educational records, strong credentials in teaching, research and consultancy with brilliant profiles of publications &amp; awards.</p>', '', '', '', '', '2022-03-10 17:13:19', '2022-03-10 17:20:42'),
(56, 'AMBEDKAR INSTITUTE OF HIGHER EDUCATION', NULL, 'ambedkar-institute-of-higher-education', '', NULL, 5, 169, '164792975292.png', '164792975255.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Ambedkar Institute of Higher Education has grown to become one of the best educational entities in Patna, Bihar and is recognized for excellence in provisional Paramedical and Nursing Education,with the solitary motive to give a big bost to the program of standard &amp; qualitative teaching primarly in paramedical and Nursing.<br />\r\nOur Institute has been doing a commendable Job in Serving the masses for more than one and half decade. The Demand for professionally trained personnel in the large and ever expanding field of Para-Medical Services has transcended geographical boundaries and its demand is now increasingly felt far from remote villages to the distant leading developed countries as well. It is in this context that Ambedkar Institute of Higher Education, Patna, for the preceding several years, with a team of dedicated and experienced faculty members, has been imparting a standard training program in useful Para-Medical sectors, in a congenial academic environment aiming at cultivating excellence in the participant trainees &amp; placing their excellence towards the services of the community &amp; the nation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being among the best institutes for paramedical and nursing in patna,through our sincere efforts and dedication to the cause, have developed excellent infrastructure and requisite resource to carry out such tasks quite effectively as per national standards and global norms.For this sincer effort on our part we at present stands where we worth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"AMBEDKAR INSTITUTE OF HIGHER EDUCATION\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Bihar\",\"city\":\"Patna\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h3>FACILITIES EXTENDED BY THE INSTITUTE</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Scholarship Facility:</strong>&nbsp;Scholarship facilities SC/ ST and OBC students have special scholarship facility. Poor boys from the General Category are also provided scholarship as per merit test. In this regard, the students are required to submit the relevant Residential &amp; Caste Certificate along with income certificate of the parents.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Hostel Facility:</strong>&nbsp;Hotel Facilities are being made available separately to boys &amp; girls, students. Cent-percent hostel facility is provided to all the girl&#39;s candidates in Nursing and Para-Medical courses in the institute premises itself. At the same time the willing male students are being provided with suitable hostel facility in separate campus.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Transport Facility:</strong>&nbsp;Our students are being extended transportation facility to take them to Govt. hospitals and eminent Nursing homes for practical cum observation facility. We also provide this facility to Para- Medical students for outdoor training and excursion trips.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cultural Activities:</strong>&nbsp;From time to time, on the occasion of inauguration and concluding of the academic session as well as on some occasions of national importance such as Gandhi Jayantee, Republic Day, Independence Day, Dr. Ambedkar&#39;s Jayantee etc. various cultural activities are undertaken in the institutes&#39; premises and our students actively participate in these programmes. This interaction among the students beings forth the natural talents in them and help in the personality development of students.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Symposiums &amp; Seminars:</strong>&nbsp;Symposiums &amp; Seminars are organized at regular intervals on different topics concerning science &amp; relevant important topics in which the students&#39; professionals &amp; prominent personalities actively participate in the deliberations. Our main objective behind holding such deliberations is to bring about a mass awareness among the masses &amp; create interest in scientific learning&#39;s.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sports &amp; games Facility:</strong>&nbsp;A specious common Room, located in the centre of the premises, provides several indoor games facilities to the students such as carom, chess, table-tennis etc. Besides the academic premises have a multi-purpose ground where students enjoy playing volleyball, badminton etc with eases &amp; comfort.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Library &amp; Reference Section:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><strong>Library &amp; Reference Section:</strong>&nbsp;It comprises a collection of authentic books on different trades. Journals, Magazines, CDs &amp; News Paper for the benefit of the trainees.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Computer Lab Faculty:&nbsp;</strong>We have a well equipped Computer Lab, with Wi-Fi facilities for the benefit of the students.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Educational &amp; Excursion Trips:</strong>&nbsp;From time to time, tours to places of academic and technical interests are arranged by the institute as per academic requirements of the courses and to keep the students afresh in their studies.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Laboratory Facility:</strong>&nbsp;One distinguishing feature of this institute is the possession of well equipped and properly maintained clinics and laboratories in the sphere of various Para-Medical sectors &amp;other relevant useful trades. We will be developing &amp; enriching these labs as per the requirements of the courses &amp; the demand of modern technologies. Our final Endeavour is to develop these labs into one of the idea laboratories in the state in its specialized field.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Medical Facility:</strong>&nbsp;Health check up of the students is being carried out by the institute at regular intervals. We organize health awareness campaign in the area and also from time hold free Health checkup camps in backward &amp; rural area as well.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>OUR VISION FOR THE NEAR FUTURE</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We have a double storied spacious building at Durgadih, Bikramganj, Rohtas with a 100 Bed capacity. This is being strengthened with furniture&#39;s equipments, accessories and requisite technical man-power association. The proposed hospital is going to operate shortly in the area.</li>\r\n	<li>We are soon going to introduce a 100 Bed Super Specialty Hospital at Danapur Patna with specialization in gynecology &amp; child diseases.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Compliance to the Code of Conduct-</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is a code of conduct for the participant trainees in different courses and they are required to strictly follow &amp; comply to the guidelines &amp; instructions as issued by the institute from time to time. Otherwise it may invite disciplinary &amp; penal actions against the defaulting student.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>EXAMINATIONS:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCandidates having less three 80% attendance in classes and less than 50% marks in internal examination may be debarred from appearing in the final examination. The examination will be held as per schedule fixed up by the Deptt. of Health, Govt. of Bihar, Indian Nursing Council, Govt. of India or the relevant Govt. of India approved Universities in case of Management &amp; IT courses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>IDENTITY CARD:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nStudents will be issued in Identity Card and the students are supposed to always hold it till the completion of the courses. Students are desired to come to the institute along with this identity card regularly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>CERTIFICATION:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCertificates will be issued by the Deptt. of Health, Govt. of Bihar, BNRC, Indian Nursing Council &amp; the Govt. of India approved universities as per relevance of the courses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>ANTI-RAGGING UNDERTAKING</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll candidates selected for admission and their parents &amp; guardians will be required to give a combined undertaking that he/ she was not involved in any activity in the past and that he/ she would not indulge in it for future. If the undertaking is violated, the students would be liable to be expelled even (Directives of the Hon. Supreme court of India)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Annexure :- 1</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nUndertaking from the students as per the provisions of anti ragging by the Hon. Supreme Court of India. I Mr./Ms. &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. Selected to Para-Medical/ Nursing/ Mamt. /IT Courses in &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; at &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. Do hereby undertake on this day &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; month &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.. year &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.the following with respect to above subject.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>That I understand the directives of the Honorable Supreme Court of India an anti ragging.</li>\r\n	<li>That I understand the meaning of Ragging and know that the ragging in any form is a punishable offence and the same is banned by the Court of Law.</li>\r\n	<li>That I have not been found or changed for my involvement in any kind of ragging in the past. However, I undertake to face disciplinary action/ legal proceedings including expulsion from the institute if the charges are found to be true or the facts in this regard are concealed, at any stage in future.</li>\r\n	<li>That I shall not resort to ragging in any form at anyplace and shall abide by the rules/ leas prescribed by the Courts, State / Union Government and the Institute authorities for the purpose from time to time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Signature of Student</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Signature of Mother / Father and or Guardian</strong>I hereby fully endorse undertaking made by my child / ward.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>STRIKING OFF NAME FROM THE ROLLS</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Termination of admission on the ground of submission of false / forged documents</li>\r\n	<li>Any kind of misconduct or indiscipline in the institute, Library, Lab, Hostel &amp; during the outdoor training.</li>\r\n	<li>Any type of criminal / communal activity</li>\r\n	<li>Regular absence for 40 days from the classes &amp; failure to pay timely, the fees, fines, rent and other charges etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Including in any sort of political, anti-social &amp; anti national activities</li>\r\n	<li>Indulging in ragging or drug addiction etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>RIGHTS RESERVED</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Managing Committee of institute reserves the right to change the requirements for admission and to introduce changes, addition in the course contents, fee charges, regulations concerning the students, or to make any other suitable modification deemed necessary in the overall interests of the institute. Rules may also be changed by the Management when needed or as per directions / instructions of the Deptt. of Health, Govt. of Bihar, Indian Nursing Council Govt. of India &amp; the relevant Govt. of India approved Universities in case of professional courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>DISPUTES</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Legal jurisdiction i.e. in case of any dispute the decision of the management will be final and binding and if there arises any dispute, it will be subject to the jurisdiction of Patna High Court, Patna only.</p>', '3.6', '', '', '', '2022-03-10 17:35:54', '2022-03-22 11:20:36');
