(57, 'G.H.G KHALSA COLLEGE  OF PHARMACY', NULL, 'ghg-khalsa-college--of-pharmacy-', '', NULL, 28, 603, '164691418391.png', '164691418373.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'NBA', '', '', '', '1984', '', '', '<h2>VISION</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To impart knowledge, develop skill and competencies in students in the field of Pharmaceutical Sciences and Pharmacy Practice. To develop academic excellence in the region and create job opportunities for rural youth. To develop, promote and nurture research activities in Pharmaceutical Sciences and Pharmacy Practice. Translating research into healthcare practice is a cornerstone of our vision. To serve the society for improvement of health and perform ethical practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>MISSION</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To be a leader in Pharmaceutical education and to attain continuous professional development. To produce Pharmacists of Excellence as responsible members of healthcare team. To promote teaching and learning process that yields state of art advancement in the pharmacy education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G.H.G. Khalsa College of Pharmacy, Gurusur Sadhar (Ludhiana) was established in 1984 under the aegis of governing Council, G.H.G. Khalsa College, Gurusur Sadhar (Ludhiana), a registered body already running two premier reputed Higher Education Institutions (HIE) in rural Punjab. The college is housed in a magnificent three storeyed building with 42,000 sq. ft. roofed area designed by Sh. H.S. Chopra, Formerly Additional Chief Architect Punjab. The foundation of this building was laid by H. E. Sh V.V Giri, President of India in 1971. This building was primarily meant to accommodate Post Graduate Regional Rural Center. However the management soon felt the better utility of the same to start job/application oriented courses relevant to the needs of rural , downtrodden and weaker sections of society and hence a two year Diploma Course in Pharmacy was introduced to begin with. A rare combination of life President Late S. Bakhtawar Singh Gill, a selfless and devoted social worker with a deep sense of architectural acumen ship and mission, and founder Principal S. Manjit Singh Khattra with a unique commitment and highly distinguished sense of educational administration and planning, the project of establishing and running this institution culminated into a grand success. Dr. Sukhdev Singh, Formerly Professor &amp; Head, Department of pharmacology, Govt. Rajindera Medical College and Hospital, Patiala, contribution his mite as head of the Department in the academic pursuits and setup of this institution at its embryonic stage. Though the expert committee of AICTE suggested the up gradation of the college to degree level in 1994, but the, management by taking its own time in a phased manner to establish, maintain and run new courses/classes on self financing and non profitable basis, introduced a four year Bachelor in Pharmacy degree course w.e.f. 2001-2002 session. The present managerial and administrative team headed by Sh. Manjit Singh Gill, President, Government Council, is putting in its earnest efforts to achieve the objectives of the college. The lush green surroundings with a rich display of its flora, the college presents a virtual feast to the eyes and synchronizes with the word of Sh. Prem Bhatia, Formerly Editor-in-chief, The Tribune group newspaper as under: &quot;A Wonder in Rural Setting&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"G.H.G KHALSA COLLEGE  OF PHARMACY\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Punjab\",\"city\":\"Ludhiana\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>AVAILABLE&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GIRLS HOSTEL&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BOYS HOSTEL&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LIBRARY&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LABORATORY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CAMPUS&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HOCKEY ASTRO TURF&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GROUND</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NIHANG SAMSHER SINGH STADIUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BASKETBALL COURT TURF</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GYMNASIUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ATM&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '<p>DOCUMENTS REQUIRED FOR ADMISSION</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Four recent passport size photographs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Birth Certificate (Matric Certificate).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Certificate of the last exam passed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Character Certificate from the institute last attended.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Aadhar Card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Reserve Category Certificate (OBC/SC/Ex-Servicemen/Sports etc.) along with Annual Income Affidavit duly attested by Class-I Magistrate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Punjab Residence Certificate. 8. Blood Group Certificate.</p>', '2022-03-10 17:58:35', '2022-03-10 18:09:43'),
(58, 'KUSUMRAJ COLLEGE OF PHARMACY', NULL, 'kusumraj-college-of-pharmacy', '', NULL, 2, 90, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'PPU (PATLIPUTRA COUNCIL OF INDIA) , NEW DELHI , GOVT. OF BIHAR (D.PHARMA)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<h2>About&nbsp;Us</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Kusumraj Institute of Pharmacy is a cutting-edge learning institution based in Patna, Bihar, recognized &amp; approved by the PCI (Pharmacy Council of India), New Delhi. We are a modern &amp; progressive pharmaceutical training college affiliated to PPU (Patliputra University) for Bachelor in Pharmacy (B. Pharm) &amp; the Health Department, Government of Bihar for Diploma in Pharmacy (D. Pharm) courses respectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Kusumraj Institute of Pharmacy, we are passionately driven about imparting excellent Pharmacy education along with the real-life practical training essential for the best future prospects of our trainees. The working principle at our respected institution involves grooming and developing trained Pharmaceutical experts and being recognized as an ideal training ground for budding Pharmacy professionals that allows students to experiment and bring to practice what they have learned in theory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Vision</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We envision it to be the ultimate destination for education, training, and research in pharmaceutical sciences and allied sectors, thereby catering to the healthcare needs of the people in the region and the whole nation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Mission</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work with the mission to groom and produce strong leaders, administrators, and officials who can take up major responsibilities as pharmaceutical professionals, with expertise surpassing the community, industry, and institutional healthcare standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Objective</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To provide infrastructure and research facilities to disseminate advanced knowledge and training to the students in various branches of Pharmaceutical sciences.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To inculcate innovative teaching-learning processes with an inter-disciplinary approach to ensure the growth of holistic wisdom acquiring all kinds of practical knowledge.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To educate and train capable manpower for the development of our country and establish linkages with the Pharmaceutical industry to promote research and development.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To promote the spirit of internationalism and competitiveness among students for the development of fresh ideas, discoveries, and inventions for a stronger society.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To encourage self-confidence, self-respect, and self-dependence among students to instill moral values making them well disciplined.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&gt;</strong>&nbsp;To pay special attention to the improvement of socio-economic conditions and support the welfare of the general population from the healthcare point of view.</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"KUSUMRAJ COLLEGE OF PHARMACY\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Andhra Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Medak\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>SPACIOUS PARKING</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPEN HERBAL GARDEN&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PHARMACEUTICAL CHEMISTRY LAB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PHARMACEUTICAL LAB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PHARMACOLOGY LAB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>COMPUTER LAB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MACHINE LAB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HUGE SEMINAR HALL&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DIGITAL &amp; OFFLINE LIBRARY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', '2022-03-10 18:24:24', '2022-03-10 18:28:22'),
(59, 'SNS VIDYAPEETH', NULL, 'sns-vidyapeeth', '', NULL, 5, 152, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '3 ACRES', '', '2019', '', '', '<p><em><strong>SNS Vidyapeeth</strong></em>, A multi functional&nbsp;educational entity which is dedicated to serve the overall development of every individual irrespective of their situation and try to enhance excellence in all aspects with an affordable high class structure.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A foundation, which is always working intensively with its various units, for the optimum and overall social, cultural and educational development of the society.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We aim to serve astronomic contribution prominently in the field of education &amp; excellence, where we are dedicated to serve the overall development of every individual irrespective of their situation and try to enhance excellence in all aspects with an affordable high-class structure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work on the different scales and methodology of education. We teach, evaluate and then brush up the skills of each individual in order to build up professional attitude as per the high-class industry standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Education is not the preparation for life but it is a Life-changing tool. So, our esteemed mentors ensure the quality education with well equipped classrooms and innovative methodology. Our affordable courses with high-class infrastructure help even the deprived students to instate the facilitation which is actually their right and we help them achieve it.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SNS VIDYAPEETH\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Bihar\",\"city\":\"East Champaran\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma,GNM\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a library facility for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has an auditorium facility for events and seminar.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>The college has a transport facility for students and staff.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The college has a departmental based laboratories facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Convenience Store\r\n	<p>The college has the convenience store facility for students.(like photocopying facility &amp; stationery etc.)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Parking Facility\r\n	<p>The college has a parking facility</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Room\r\n	<p>The college has a guest house/waiting room facilities for visiting faculty and student family members.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Banks Facilities\r\n	<p>The college has the Banks/ATM facilities for all students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '', '', '', '2022-03-11 11:56:40', '2022-03-11 15:42:20'),
(60, 'RAMA DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'rama-dental-college-', '', NULL, 33, 790, '164786123319.png', '164786123337.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'UGC', '', '150 Acres', '170', '2014', '', '3816', '<h3>Vision</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To emerge as a Global Premier University in imparting education of international standards, to build superior professionals with strong work ethics and to empower the world with futuristic minds, through excellence in research and innovation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Mission</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To promote national and international collaboration for industry academia integration to achieve top most position in global hierarchy.</li>\r\n	<li>To create a scientific, challenging, transparent and sustainable environment/curriculum ideal for research, innovation, entrepreneurship and consultancy.</li>\r\n	<li>To nurture talent and creativity, committed to serve people, society and nation at large.</li>\r\n	<li>To inculcate strong morals, values &amp; ethics to build socially committed and spiritually inspired personalities.</li>\r\n	<li>To empower and uplift each section of society through education and to contribute back to the environment by adapting and promoting eco-friendly practices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Core Values</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We, at all the Rama Group companies and institutions respect the Indian core value system and practice it in our daily lives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Dharma</em>&nbsp;- Righteousness</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Arth&nbsp;</em>- Creation of wealth for the betterment of individual and society at large</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Karma</em>&nbsp;- Commitment to duty</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"RAMA DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Kanpur Nagar\",\"degree\":\"BDS,GNM,ANM\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>It strives to provide a homely and secure environment to the students. The campuses have separate hostels for boys. The hostels are fully furnished and well ventilated along with all the modern amenities to provide a comfortable stay for the students. Besides, having a serene environment for a healthy and productive life, hostels also have a common room, 24-hours internet facility, telephone facility and a mess facility that serves healthy and nutritious food to the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>It strives to provide a homely and secure environment to the students. The campuses have separate hostels for girls. The hostels are fully furnished and well ventilated along with all the modern amenities to provide a comfortable stay for the students. Besides, having a serene environment for a healthy and productive life, hostels also have a common room, 24-hours internet facility, telephone facility and a mess facility that serves healthy and nutritious food to the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The University has a Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a library facility for all students. Books: 63279, Journals: 265, Journals Of Volume: 11270, Book Cd: 2832, Bound Journals: 680, Cassettes/ Floppy: 222, Journals Cd: 266, Thesis/ Dissertation: 526, Newspapers: 32, Who Books: 810, Project Report: 107.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>University promotes holistic learning where equal stress is laid on sports and extra-curricular activities. The Sports facilities at the campuses are at par with international standards. The facilities cater to Cricket, Football, Athletics, Swimming, Hockey, Volleyball, Basket Ball, Badminton, Tennis, and Squash. Students are constantly encouraged to indulge in physical activities to inculcate a healthy and active lifestyle.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The campus has a large auditorium with seating capacity of more than 1200 people. The acoustic and light arrangement of the auditorium makes the seminars, workshops and other activities a pleasing experience.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The University has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Wifi<br />\r\n	The campuses are equipped with Wi-Fi to provide connectivity to the students as well as faculty members.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The IT facilities are fed with fiber optics and are supported by multiple IBM servers to ensure all-round connectivity. Besides, frequent IT workshops and seminars keep students and faculty abreast with latest technological advancements.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Classrooms\r\n	<p>The University has the Well-furnished Classroom facility available on the campus.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>All campuses of Rama university offer multi mode transport facilities from campus to key drop points on the city. The university also operates a fleet of college buses that are fitted with GPS vehicle tracking system for the safety of the travelers. Students, faculty members, staff and visitors travelling to campuses, using their private vehicle, have ample parking space inside and outside the campuses. All campuses are also easily accessible by using public transport system. In addition, private cab services are also available that cab booked in advance.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Moot Court\r\n	<p>As a part of Juridical studies, moot court is part of college curriculum at Faculty of Juridical Sciences. Here the participants take part in simulated court or arbitration proceedings, usually involving drafting memorials or memoranda and participating in oral argument. Moot court involves a simulated appellate court (appellate advocacy) or arbitral case, which is different from a mock trial that involves a simulated jury trial or bench trial (trial advocacy).</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Alumni Associations\r\n	<p>The University has good networking for the alumni association.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Banks Facilities\r\n	<p>Campuses at Mandhana, Kanpur and Rama Delhi, Ghaziabad has an on-campus banking facility along with ATM machines to provide 24X7 hassle free financial transactions.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '3.8', '', '', '', '2022-03-12 13:16:36', '2022-03-21 16:14:13'),
(61, 'BAKSON HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE  & HOSPITAL', NULL, 'bakson-homoeopathic-medical-college---hospital-', '', NULL, 33, 776, '164733489948.png', '164733489955.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'CCH', '', '', '45', '2002', '', '595', '<h2><strong>The Man Behind Bakson</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr. Satinder Pal Singh Bakshi, a product of Nehru Homoeopathic Medical College, New Delhi, is known for his dedication and zeal to spread Homoeopathy as a scientific, alternative, effective and viable system of medicine in our country. By virtue of his professional standing and academic acumen, he became the youngest President of Central Council of Homoeopathy (Govt. of India) at the age of 39 years and occupied this coveted post for 18 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Homoeopathic education in India witnessed phenomenal change during his tenure, under his able guidance. He was not only instrumental in rationalising homoeopathic education in India but also introduced the concepts of quality and accountability in homoeopathic practice by initiating amendments to the Homoeopathic Practitioners (Professional Etiquettes, Conduct and Code of Ethics) Regulations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr. Bakshi is the founder Chairman of Bakson Drugs &amp; Pharmaceuticals Pvt. Ltd., a leading homoeopathic drug manufacturing and marketing company. Dr. Bakshi has also to his credit the establishment of a nationwide chain of Bakson&#39;s Homoeopathy Clinics known for treating various disorders, including Allergy. He has treated more than a million patients over his 38 years of long professional career.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To translate his dream of achieving excellence in homoeopathic education, Dr. S. P. S. Bakshi established Bakson Homoeopathic Medical College &amp; Hospital, a renowned institute with a sprawling campus in lush green environment of Knowledge Park, Greater Noida. It confers degrees to budding doctors in the field of Homoeopathy at Undergraduate and Postgraduate level.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"BAKSON HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE  & HOSPITAL\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Gautam Buddha Nagar\",\"degree\":\"BHMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>COLLEGE&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Reception&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative block&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Lecture Hall</li>\r\n	<li>Seminar Hall</li>\r\n	<li>Library&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>GYM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>HOSPITAL&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Administrative Block&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>O.P.D</li>\r\n	<li>I.P.D</li>\r\n	<li>Emergency/I.C.U/O.T.</li>\r\n	<li>Physiotherapy&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Yoga&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Naturopathy&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Skin And Hair</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '164733671317.pdf', '', '', '2022-03-15 14:01:39', '2022-03-15 14:31:53'),
(62, 'MAHARISHI MENHI HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE & HOSPITAL', NULL, 'maharishi-menhi-homoeopathic-medical-college--hospital-', '', NULL, 5, 159, '164733908125.png', '164733908116.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '8 ACRES', '31', '1980', '', '208', '<h2>Welcome to Maharshi Menhi<br />\r\nHomoeopathic Medical College And Hospital</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MAHARSHI MENHI HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE &amp; HOSPITAL was established on 29th April 1980 in Katihar in the name of pious saint MAHARSHI MENHI, under the Governing Body. Presently, it is under the MAHARSHI MENHI CHARITABLE TRUST, KATIHAR.<br />\r\nThe Institute, affiliated to the Babasaheb Bhimrao Ambedkar Bihar University, Muzuffarpur, presently conducts the degree course in Homoeopathy viz Bachelor of Homoeopathic Medicine and Surgery [B.H.M.S.] since 1987.<br />\r\nToday it consists of an Undergraduate section with an auditorium of 300 seating capacity, a hospital having an outpatient department and a 25 bedded inpatients department along with investigative facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute is functioning in its own campus measuring about 6 acres of land atJeewachh Nagar, Katihar, Bihar- 854105 and 2 acres at Kuretha, Katihar, with a total floor space of more than50 thousand square metres with effect from 11.08.2016.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"MAHARISHI MENHI HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE & HOSPITAL\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Bihar\",\"city\":\"Katihar\",\"degree\":\"BHMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The college has a Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The Library &amp; Student Help Desk division provides books and all necessary information concerning scholarship and other information is taken care of by efficient library staff. At present, there are more than 2300 books and 05 subscribed journals in the library. Presently all the UG departments also have Departmental Library.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The college has sports facilities for all students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has an auditorium facility for events and seminars.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has an IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>A well-equipped clinical laboratory, radiology including ultra-sound facilities are available at the college for effective diagnosis and treatment of the patients attending the outpatient and inpatient departments. Clinical Pathological Laboratory:- It has a Laboratory where we conduct basic Lab investigations like Hematology tests, Biochemistry Tests, Urine tests and Pregnancy tests, etc. Samples tested:- Blood, Urine, Stool, Sputum, Semen, etc., Biochemistry Tests - Blood glucose, Serum Cholesterol, HDL, Triglycerides, Lipid profile, Urea, Creatinine, Uric acid, SGOT, SGPT &amp; Total Bilirubin. Hematology Tests &ndash; Hemoglobin, TLC, RBC Count, DC, PCV, MCV, MCH, MCHC, AEC, Platelet, E.S.R, BT, CT Urine, and Stool - R.E &amp; Microscopic Examination. Microbiology Tests &ndash; Urine Pregnancy Test</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Room\r\n	<p>The college has guest house/waiting room facilities for visiting faculty and student family members.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '', '', '', '2022-03-15 15:11:21', '2022-03-15 15:54:59'),
(63, 'MAGADH HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'magadh-homoeopathic-medical-college', '', NULL, 5, 167, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '', '1969', '', '', '<p>Magadh Homoeopathic Medical College Nalanda, Bihar, is one of the reputed Private&nbsp;Homoeopathic Colleges in Bihar. The college is popularly known as M.H.M.C. Nalanda&nbsp;and was founded in the year 1969. This famous M.H.M.C. Nalanda in Bihar&nbsp;is affiliated to B.R.Ambedkar Bihar University, Muzaffarpur and is approved by the Central Council of Indian Medicines.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"MAGADH HOMOEOPATHIC MEDICAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Bihar\",\"city\":\"Nalanda\",\"degree\":\"BHMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h3><strong>Facilities</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Library</td>\r\n			<td>Auditorium</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hostel</td>\r\n			<td>Cafeteria</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Laboratory</td>\r\n			<td>Hospital / Medical Facility</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '4', '', '', '', '2022-03-15 16:11:05', '2022-03-15 16:41:26'),
(64, 'PATANJALI AYURVED COLLEGE', NULL, 'patanjali-ayurved-college-', '', NULL, 34, 827, '164734541670.png', '164734541682.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '67', '2006', '', '514', '<p>&quot;In year 1932 at the divine seat of Haridwar, on the bank of holy river &#39;Mother Ganga&#39; the great visionary, his holiness P.P.Swami Kripalu Dev ji Maharaj started&#39;Vishwa Jnana Mandir&#39; which later on became famous as &#39;Kripalu Bag Ashram&#39;. This Ashram was a centre of revolutionist and sheltered Ras Bihari Bose and others who scarificed their life during the struggle of freedom. From this very place, on 15th january 1995, Swami Ramdev ji Maharaj and Acharya Balkrishna Ji Maharaj under the patronage of Pujya Swami Shankar dev Ji Maharaj, established Divya Yoga Mandir (Trust) and started their services to mankind.Focusing on preservation and promotion of health and to serve the ailing huminity, a college of Ayurveda &#39;Patanjali Bhartiya Ayurvigyan Evam Anusandhan Sansthan&#39; has been established by Divya Yoga Mandir (Trust) to produce skilled human brings Ayurvedic Physicians. The college is situated in a very peaceful environment surrounded by lush green area on the Delhi-Haridwar National</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"PATANJALI AYURVED COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttaranchal\",\"city\":\"Haridwar\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The college has a Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a well-equipped library comprising of books related to Ayurveda, Yoga, Unani &amp; Siddha as well as modern Medical Sciences. It has got a wide range of Journals and Magazines of National and International standards. There is a reading room with a seating capacity of 80 students and a Cyber-caf&eacute;.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The college has sports facilities for all students. There is a large playground for the students in the walled area of a college campus for sports and other recreational activities.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>There is a big canteen with name DANA-PANI in the college campus area providing a wide range of Indian snacks and pure vegetarian eatables.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The college has an auditorium facility for events and seminars.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with a first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has an excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The college has a departmental based laboratory facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Room\r\n	<p>The college has a guest house/waiting room facilities for visiting faculty and student family members.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '', '', '', '2022-03-15 16:49:07', '2022-03-15 16:58:42'),
(65, 'ERAM UNANI MEDICAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'eram-unani-medical-college-', '', NULL, 33, 796, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'CCIM', '', '', '', '2004', '', '256', '<p>Lucknow the capital of Uttar Pradesh does not have an active minority Unani Medical College. Although this historical city has a State Unani Medical College, known as the TAKMIL-UT- TIB COLLEGE, which came into existence by the endeavours of ATTIBAYE&rsquo; JHAWAI TOLA, (Unani Physicians/Hakims) Lucknow. The rein of this Institute was in the hands of Muslim Minority intelligentsia, but with the curse of time, and circumstances, and the ill concieved efforts of its staff to change its status, opened the door for its nationalisation by the Government of U. P and subsequently it was affiliated with the Kanpur University. Thus this one and the only minority Unani Institution was converted into a government institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moved by this loss, the Eram Educational Society seriously pondered over the need of re-establising such a College for rendering valuable services to those poor &ldquo;sick&rdquo;, who were unable to afford the costly allopathic treatment, and decided to open a Unani Medical College at Kursi Road. Thanks to the Almighty that it has come in to existence in a four storeyed gigantic building. In consultation with, and under the guidance of educational experts and experienced doctors, the work of imparting education to students and treatment of parents through Unani medicines is being successfully done. The College boasts of multifarious departments with necessary infrastructure. equipment and faculty. besides having the facility of Hostels, which are a basic feature for any seat of learing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eram Unani Medical College Kursi Road Lucknow is recognized by the Central Council of Indian Medicine and is affiliated to Chhatarpati Shahu Ji Maharaj University, Kanpur, and is imparting education in Unani Medicine &amp; Surgery for B U. M. S. (Kamil-e-Tib-o-Jarahat) as per courses duly approved by C.C.I.M., under the auspices of Eram Educational Society in own building. Here students of the country or from abroad can seek admission irrespective of religion, caste, creed, colour or sex.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College imparts education in Unani Medicines &amp; Surgery and under takes research work in this field. The students are to be given extensive knowledge of the fundamental theories &amp; basic principles of Unani system of medicine i.e. logic, philosophy coupled with history of Unani medicine, modern medical approach on subjects of Physiology, Preventive and Social Medicine, Pharmacology, Pathology &amp; Bacteriology, Bed side Clinic/Saririyat, Toxicology, Anatomy, Medical Jurisprudence etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"ERAM UNANI MEDICAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Lucknow\",\"degree\":\"BUMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility which provides good hostel accommodation for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a library facility for all students. A well furnished nicely maintained Library in a very spacious Hall exists in the College. The same is operating under a Qualified Librarian, with approximately 4000 books. It is also supported by Medical Dictionaries &amp; other Medical Journals for the benefit of the teachers and the taught.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health centre with a first aid facility for the students. Eram Unani Medical College consists of a 150 bedded Unani Hospital and another 150 bedded Allopathic Hospital. Both these Hospitals have necessary infrastructure equipment, Teaching Faculty and a Team of Physicians/ Surgeons to look after the O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. departments. Necessary laboratories with the required number of technicians and other staff are also available for serving the patients. Both the Hospitals are running for quite some time. A diagnostic Center and a separate Eram Unani Research Center are also functioning in the College, besides a Center for Heart diseases.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has an IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The college has a departmental based laboratories&nbsp;facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', '2022-03-15 17:02:21', '2022-03-15 17:17:29'),
(66, 'MAHARISHI AUROBINDO SUBHARTI COLLEGE & HOSPITAL OF NATUROPATHY & YOGIC SCIENCES', NULL, 'maharishi-aurobindo-subharti-college--hospital-of-naturopathy--yogic-sciences', '', NULL, 33, 802, '164740937493.png', '164740937442.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'CONSTITUENT', '', '250 ACRES', '', '2011', '', '', '<p>Health care&nbsp;world over has shifted towards more&nbsp;Natural methods of treatments&nbsp;&amp; is now focusing on Holistic approach or the&nbsp;Mind Body medicine. New frontiers in&nbsp;Integrative medicine&nbsp;have proven beneficial to heal individuals more effectively &amp; people are beginning to appreciate the benefits of using natural healing therapies. A 2008 study by the National Center for Complementary and Alternative Medicine (NCCAM) found 38 percent of adults and 12 percent of children in the U.S. use some form of alternative medicine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naturopathic medicine&nbsp;is based on the concept of treating the body with&nbsp;Panchamahabhuthas&nbsp;that is Earth, Water, Fire, Air and Ether which forms the basic constituents of the body. Naturopathy promotes the body to rejuvenate and recover by facilitating its own healing capacity by providing and enabling a favorable internal mechanism in the physical and mental sphere, revitalize and rejuvenate the body and strengthen the immune system against the disease causing agents present in and around individuals. It also educates and empowers individuals to make lifestyle changes necessary for the best possible health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yoga&nbsp;is now worldwide accepted evidence based system of healing owing to its holistic &amp; integrated concept of approach and suitability for all age groups. Its simplicity of application &amp; cost effectiveness has brought a tremendous change in the&nbsp;Medical field. Both Naturopathy &amp; Yoga work wonderfully in&nbsp;prevention, treatment &amp; rehabilitation&nbsp;when scientifically applied. Their complementary nature, safety, lack of adverse effects, cost effectiveness &amp; simplicity have made them popular in the medical fraternity &amp; accepted in the&nbsp;world&rsquo;s best Health care&nbsp;setups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in 2011 Maharishi Aurobindo Subharti College &amp; Hospital of Naturopathy &amp; Yogic Sciences, Meerut is a constituent college of Swami Vivekanand Subharti University backed by the SKKB Charitable Trust. It is the first institurion of its kind in North India. The College thrives for producing quality doctors of Naturopathic Medicine &amp; Yoga Therapy. Hence the academic program has been developed to ensure that students have the opportunity to build a strong foundation and to demonstrate competency in each major modality involved in Lifestyle Modification, Natural Therapies, Mind Body medicine, Integrative Medicine &amp; Chronic disease management &amp; Rehabilitation. The students from various parts of the country &amp; abroad have a conducive atmosphere to emerge as successful achievers in the field. The college supports all-round personality development through cultural programs, sports events, moral codes, ragging free environment &amp; a supportive approach.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"MAHARISHI AUROBINDO SUBHARTI COLLEGE & HOSPITAL OF NATUROPATHY & YOGIC SCIENCES\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Meerut\",\"degree\":\"BNYS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a boy&rsquo;s hostel facility There are 14 hostels including 2 NRI hostels within the Subharti University Campus. The hostels maintain strict timings of entry. All hostels have a resident warden and also a chief warden (Girls/Boys Separate) for the proper management &amp; care of the students.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The college has a girl&#39;s hostel facility There are 14 hostels including 2 NRI hostels within the Subharti University Campus. The hostels maintain strict timings of entry. All hostels have a resident warden and also a chief warden (Girls/Boys Separate) for the proper management &amp; care of the students.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>The college has are two well-equipped Gymnasiums on the University campus for Boys and one Gym is for Girls, there are separate Couches in GYM for Boys and Girls.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a library is spacious enough to cater not only to the existing needs but also accommodates resources &amp; services for future requirements. There is a continuous effort to update &amp; add to our study material resources. &nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The college has a view of all-round development of the students, liberal arrangements have been made in the way of indoor, outdoor games and sports facilities for boys and girls so as to provide them with ample competitive and recreational opportunities.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students. SVS-University Offers an excellent choice of places to eat within the University campus. University Houses Six Canteens which offer Multi-Cuisine Menus ranging from Indian to Continental and Chinese in a Modern and Hygienic ambiance, with one exclusively for Girls. For Snakes, Juices, Beverages, and other Indian and Continental fast foods, there are three Modern Cafeterias on the University Campus.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The College has a State of the Art Auditoriums facility. The campus has two other auditoriums with a seating capacity of around 500, each air-cooled and air-conditioned respectively, besides possessing two multi-purpose halls which are used for diverse activities such as seminars, symposia, debates, cultural activities, movies shows/previews/etc. Also, each college has an individual counseling room, seminar room &amp; and auditorium for their Individual events.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has a health center with Medicare and Denticare Facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi\r\n	<p>The college has a Wi-Fi facility for the students and staff.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The college has an excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>The college has a transport facility for students and staff.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The college has Well equipped laboratories for basic sciences with a separate Anatomy dissection hall and museum that offer a wide exposure to the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Convenience Store\r\n	<p>The college has to meet the daily requisites of students and residents of our campus, there are in campus departmental stores, grocery stores, ticket booking counter, cobbler shop, Indian postal services, medical store, stationery shop, hairdresser, and many more.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Alumni Associations\r\n	<p>The college has good networking for the alumni association.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Banks Facilities\r\n	<p>The college has a branch of Oriental Bank of Commerce that has been set within the premises of the University, which offers all kinds of National and International Banking Facilities, including education loans to students on easy terms if desired. Apart from regular banking services to the students and the employees of the University, there are three Banks that provide ATM Facilities to facilitate access to Bank Accounts round clock cash withdrawal. &middot; Oriental Bank of Commerce. &middot; Punjab National&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.7', '164741650418.pdf', '', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"5\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">IMPORTANT INFORMATION &amp; DOCUMENT CHECKLIST</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:99%\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>1.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>New Session of BNYS 1st&nbsp;year will commence from 1st August.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>2.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>Your Fee dues for the upcoming year shall have to be clear.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>3.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>Following documents are mandatory to be submitted at the time of admission. If you have not already submitted any of the following documents till now please get them for submission.</p>\r\n\r\n						<p>In addition:<br />\r\n						a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Photocopy of marks sheet &amp; certificate of 10th&nbsp;(2 Sets, self attested)&nbsp;<br />\r\n						b.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Photocopy of marks sheet &amp; certificate of 12th&nbsp;(2 Sets, self attested)<br />\r\n						c.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Original T.C/ Migration Certificate (Compulsory for CBSE) + 2 Photocopies (Self attested)<br />\r\n						d.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Photographs - Six Recent passport size Photographs of the student 2 photographs of Mother 2 photographs of Father<br />\r\n						e.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Photocopy of Self attested Aadhar card 2 copies<br />\r\n						f.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Affidavits (Matter will be provided by the College Office)<br />\r\n						g.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Photocopy of all fee Receipts/ Payments done<br />\r\n						h.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Cast Certificate (Attested by gazetted officer)</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>4.</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n						<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n						<p>Also please get the following for verification of the documents submitted.<br />\r\n						i.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Original Mark sheet &amp; certificate of 10th. (For Verification only)<br />\r\n						ii.&nbsp;&nbsp;Original Mark sheet &amp; certificate of 12th. (For Verification only)<br />\r\n						iii.&nbsp;Original Aadhar Card. (For Verification only)</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '2022-03-16 10:42:54', '2022-03-16 12:46:23');
