(67, 'IIMT UNIVERSITY ,MEERUT', NULL, 'iimt-university-meerut-', '', NULL, 33, 802, '164741849383.png', '164741849359.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'UGC', '', '100 ACRES', '1340', '2016', '', '4390', '<h2>Vision</h2>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>To be a world - class university imparting knowledge and values and providing students, an excellent learning experience through research &amp; innovation in the field of Science, Technology, Management and other areas that will meet the aspirations of world community.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<blockquote><strong>Mission</strong></blockquote>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>University stands for academic, professional and ethical empowerment of the youths by using the state-of-the-art technology, time-tested and innovative concepts, excellent infrastructure and internationally acclaimed facilitators.</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"IIMT UNIVERSITY ,MEERUT\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Meerut\",\"degree\":\"BAMS,BNYS,B. Pharma,ANM\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The University has a boy&#39;s hostel facility. All hostels are self-contained with more than 1500 rooms in total with the capacity of 3000 students on a twin&ndash;sharing basis. Hostel facilities include excellent dining halls, indoor games, Wi-Fi internet connectivity and fields for outdoor games, separate gym for boys and girls, reading room, medical aid room, and Laundry Facility, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The University has a girl&#39;s hostel facility. All hostels are self-contained with more than 1500 rooms in total with the capacity of 3000 students on a twin&ndash;sharing basis. Hostel facilities include excellent dining halls, indoor games, Wi-Fi internet connectivity and fields for outdoor games, separate gym for boys and girls, reading room, medical aid room, and Laundry Facility, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Gym\r\n	<p>IIMT University&rsquo;s gymnasium provides much modern fitness equipment with the attached dressing room. The students thus find ample opportunities for toning up their bodies and minds. Highly equipped and scientifically laid out gymnasium for the students where they can regularly see their health and fitness freaks work out to keep themselves fit is one of the attractions of the campus.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The libraries of IIMT University have a total stock of approximately 4,00,000 publications and more than 500 National and International Journals in Management, Engineering, Hotel Management, Law, Education, and Pharmacy, etc. The library also contains a rich collection of assorted material on general awareness. The University is also a member of DELNET and INDEST which provides ready access to libraries of leading institutions of the world. Librarians are relentlessly engaged in continuously augmenting our International Journals Resource Base by having EBSCO which allows access to over 4000 International Journals of repute. Online database subscriptions for data related to industries and economics are supportive research materials for faculty and students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>IMT University has always supported sports, sports events and encouraged sporting talent. For this, modern indoor and outdoor game facilities are provided and students are encouraged to participate in various sports like Cricket, Hockey, Badminton, Table Tennis, Football, Basket Ball, Volley Ball, Chess, Swimming, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The university has a unique mess in the hostels wherein a variety of Indian, Chinese, and Continental meals and snacks are served to the multiethnic tastes of the students who themselves decide their menu. Not only that, the highly qualified Hotel Management faculties further improve the quality and taste of meals, an outstanding and unique feature of the IIMT mess. Three active cafeterias ensure nutritious refreshment for busy minds. Hygienic healthy food and snacks are provided to both students and faculty members at subsidized rates. A wide variety of snacks and meals are served on demand.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>The University has an auditorium facility for events and seminars.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The University now has its own IIMT Life Line Hospital for providing 24X7 medical facility, ambulance facility, and emergency facility to all the IIMT students and staff.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The University has an excellent IT Infrastructure facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Transport\r\n	<p>The university provides excellent transport facilities for students through buses plying on all routes in the city and nearby areas as per the requirement of the students so that they have comfortable commutation to the campus. The campus dwellers feel no distance from the civic amenities through need-based plying of regular transport from campus to city.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>The University has a departmental based laboratories facility for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Swimming Pool\r\n	<p>The University has a Swimming Pool facility for all students.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Alumni Associations\r\n	<p>The IIMT University Alumni Association will provide a platform for every graduate to remain connected to his/her alma mater. IIMT University legacy proves that it has produced leaders, entrepreneurs, social entrepreneurs, artists, writers, etc and the Alumni Association binds them all together. The Association will seamlessly connect the University, faculty, students and fellow alumni to engage, energize and enhance.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Room\r\n	<p>The University has a guest house/waiting room facilities for visiting faculty and student family members.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Banks Facilities\r\n	<p>IIMT University has a tie-up with Nationalized Banks. This allows every student to open and operate an account through cheque book or debit cards. The banks are operating their own ATM machines on the campus.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.7', '', '', '', '2022-03-16 13:14:53', '2022-03-16 14:36:57'),
(68, 'DEOBAND UNANI MEDICAL COLLEGE HOSPITAL AND RESEARCH CENTRE, DEOBAND', NULL, 'deoband-unani-medical-college-hospital-and-research-centre-deoband', '', NULL, 33, 811, '164742488073.png', '164742488020.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '48', '1991', '', '118', '<table style=\"height:0px; width:98%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff; height:386px; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p>Deoband Unani Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre, Deoband, established in 1991 by founder Manager Dr. Q. Z. Qureshi, for the students seeking admission to the B.U.M.S. (Kamiil-e-Tibb-o-Jarahat) degree course. This course is prescribed according to the syllabus by C.C.I.M. Govt. of India.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Deoband Unani Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre, Deoband, is being run under supervision &amp; management of Muslim Educational and Social Welfare Association (Regd.). The Association is registered under the societies registration Act 1860, and have minority community certificate from the Minority Commission, state Govt. U.P. and have minority certificate from National Commission for Minority Educational Institutions, Govt. of India with the main objective to become a beacon of hope and self reliance for the poor, needy and deserving section of the society along with the commitment of providing Education &amp; Medical Facilities. We intend to produce competent Unani Physicians who could handle all sorts of cases medical as well as surgical based on their intensive knowledge and experience in the line. From time to time and at the time of perception of sporadic diseases camps are organized to control over the spread of diseases.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>The Institute is recognized by C.C.I.M. Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare Govt. of India. Moreover the Institution is currently affiliated with Ch. Charan Singh University, Meerut since 2015-16. Earlier it was affiliated with C.S.J.M. University, Kanpur since 1991.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>The Institution has elegant building which has well maintained 14 departments &amp; Laboratories, well equipped Pathology Lab, Museums, Lecture Theaters, Herbal Garden, Pharmacy and 150 bedded Hospital with I.P.D., O.P.D. Labour Room, X-ray, 24 hours emergency Ambulance, Operation facility, Generator facility, delivery facility etc. and highly qualified, well experienced and dedicated staff for College &amp; Hospital.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>The College provides Hostel and Mess facilities for boys &amp; girls students separately at their own expenses.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Deoband Unani Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre, Deoband, has a spacious campus with many trees and vast expanse of lawns with peaceful atmosphere for education and patient care. Every room of the college and hospital has natural light and fresh air.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Deoband Unani Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre is located 150 Km. from Delhi on Meerut-Muzaffarnagar-Deoband road. The Institution is situated at Deoband on Karanjali road near Talheri Chungi, Deoband. There are railway &amp; bus facilities available in Deoband.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Seven batches students of B.U.M.S. Degree course have passed out from the institution since 1991. They have awarded degrees of Bachelor of Unani Medicine and Surgery by Chhatrapati Shahu Ji Maharaj University, Kanpur, as per the curriculum of Central Council of Indian Medicine, New Delhi. All necessary arrangements in the interest of students welfare have been done to result oriented.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>In due course of time, a research programme shall also be projected to reach superiority &amp; latest technology in the guaranteeing easiness to which poor public could afford.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff\">\r\n			<hr /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff; height:37px\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"DEOBAND UNANI MEDICAL COLLEGE HOSPITAL AND RESEARCH CENTRE, DEOBAND\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Saharanpur\",\"degree\":\"BUMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p><strong>Library</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Books will be issued to students for a week and after this Rs. 1/- per day will be charged as Penalty.</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"height:0px; width:98%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff; height:386px; vertical-align:top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Hospital</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>150 bedded well equipped &amp; well maintained with I.P.D. &amp; O.P.D. facility a grand charitable Hospital is attached to Deoband Unani Medical College, Deoband for the purpose of training of students &amp; to serve patients. The treatment is given mostly free of cost or at reasonable cost according to severity of the patient. The treatment given to the patients is mainly based on Unani system of medicine, but adequate facilities of modern system of medicines have also been made available.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Following O.P.D.s &amp; I.P.D.s are being run in the Hospital</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Moalijat (Unani Medicines)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Amraz-e-Ain, Uzn Anaf wa Halaq (Ophthalmology &amp; ENT)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Amraz-e-Atfal (Paediatrics)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Qabalat wa Amraz-e-Niswan (Gynae &amp; Obs.) (A well furnished and well equipped labour room is being run)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Jarahat (Surgery)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Ilaj-Bit-Tadbeer (Regimental Therapy)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Tahafuzi wa Samaji Tib (Community Medicine including family welfare)</li>\r\n				<li>O.P.D. &amp; I.P.D. of Amraz-e-Jild wa Amraz-e-Zohrawiya (Skin &amp; Joint)</li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p>A well furnished &amp; well equipped Operation Theatre has been provided and minor &amp; major operations are performed by experienced and well qualified surgeons.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Casualty &amp; emergency facility are available 24 hours in the Hospital.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>X-ray facility is available.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Own Ambulance is available for 24 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Pathology Lab facility is available.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>U.S.G. &amp; E.C.G. facility is available.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Generator facility is available.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href=\"http://www.dumc.co.in/opd_ipd_2017.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">OPD and IPD Data 2017</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href=\"http://www.dumc.co.in/opd_ipd.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">OPD and IPD Data 2016</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff\">\r\n			<hr /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#e1f0ff; height:37px\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>', '3.7', '', '', '', '2022-03-16 15:01:20', '2022-03-16 15:30:57'),
(69, 'KHALSA COLLEGE OF VETERINARY & ANIMAL SCIENCES', NULL, 'khalsa-college-of-veterinary--animal-sciences', '', NULL, 28, 593, '164743039964.png', '164743039964.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><strong>Genesis of Khalsa College</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The provision of higher education to Sikhs and Punjabis within Punjab during the British Raj Period in the late 19th Century was envisioned&nbsp;by the Sikh Scholars of that time. Singh Sabha Movement and Chief&nbsp;Khalsa Diwan approached the then Sikh Maharajas and the people of Punjab to donate land and raise funds for the purpose. People of&nbsp;Amritsar, Lahore, and other cities of Punjab including rich Sikh families and the Maharajas donated land and funds for the construction of Khalsa College.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khalsa College Establishment Committee was set up&nbsp;in 1890 with Colonel W. R. M. Holroyd, Director of&nbsp;Public Instruction, Punjab, as President, and W. Bell,&nbsp;Principal of Government College, Lahore, as&nbsp;Secretary. Among the native constituents of this&nbsp;121-member committee were Sir Attar Singh, Gurdial&nbsp;Singh Maan of Nabha, Diwan Gurmukh Singh of&nbsp;Patiala, Bhai Kahn Singh, Professor Gurmukh Singh, and Sardar Jawahir Singh. Many princely states of&nbsp;British India and Sikh people of Punjab including&nbsp;Maharaja Rajendra Singh of Patiala rendered&nbsp;financial help for the establishment of Khalsa College.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>History of KCVAS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the year 2009, Khalsa College Charitable Society Governing Council thought of starting College of Veterinary and Animal Sciences to develop technically sound human resources in the field of veterinary health, animal production, and management to cater to the increasing demand of veterinarians in the state. The institution was granted NOC by the Punjab State Government to start a new veterinary and animal science college at Amritsar to start B.V.Sc. &amp; A.H. (Bachelor of Veterinary Sciences and Animal Husbandry) 5-year program. Guru Angad Dev Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (GADVASU), Ludhiana accorded affiliation in the year 2010.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr. S. K. Jand, a highly qualified, experienced, and&nbsp;dedicated Professor joined as founder Principal of&nbsp;Khalsa College of Veterinary and Animal Sciences&nbsp;(KCVAS) in February 2010. The college enrolled the&nbsp;first batch of students for the degree of B. V. Sc. &amp; A.&nbsp;H. in October 2010 with an existing staff of three&nbsp;Professors, seven Assistant Professors, and nine&nbsp;non-teaching staff. With the KCVAS building under&nbsp;construction, the College activities were initiated in&nbsp;the building of the Department of Physiotherapy,&nbsp;Khalsa College, Amritsar.&nbsp;In view of a few deficiencies in terms of infrastructure&nbsp;and faculty and in spite of best efforts by the&nbsp;management and the college staff, the permission for&nbsp;admission of the second batch of students during the&nbsp;2011- 12 session was withheld by VCI. Though there&nbsp;was no major deficiency still there prevailed an&nbsp;uncertainty even for the conduct of the annual&nbsp;examination and the students were stressed regarding&nbsp;their careers. With the constant encouragement from&nbsp;the Honorary Secretary, S. Rajinder Mohan Chinna,&nbsp;and untiring efforts by S. Ajmer Singh, Legal&nbsp;Secretary, and Dr. S. K. Jand, the Principal of KCVAS&nbsp;with the intervention of Hon&rsquo;ble Punjab &amp;&nbsp;Haryana High Court the annual examinations of&nbsp;students were timely conducted in June 2012, under&nbsp;the supervision of GADVASU, the affiliating University&nbsp;of KCVAS. Provisional admissions were again&nbsp;permitted during the 2012 -13 session.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the blessings of Wahe Guru Ji, the helping hand&nbsp;of the management, and untiring efforts of teaching and&nbsp;non-teaching staff of the college it got recognition from&nbsp;the Veterinary Council of India (VCI) and it was&nbsp;included in the 1st schedule of the Government of India&nbsp;vide Gazette Notification No, 1861 dated 3rd&nbsp;September 2015. In the year 2021, GADVASU granted permanent affiliation to the college and ICAR also granted accreditation to the college for a period of five years with a score of 3.17 for the degree program and 3.11 to the College equivalent to Grade &quot;A&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mandate:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To produce highly skilled professionals in the field of Veterinary and Animal</li>\r\n	<li>Sciences for catering to the ever-growing demand of professionals in this field.</li>\r\n	<li>To impart expert and scientific guidance to the farmers in rearing their livestock.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide state-of-the-art clinical services at Veterinary Clinical Complex (VCC) to cater to the needs of livestock farmers and pet owners of Punjab especially of the Majha region.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide entrepreneur skills to students for self-employment in the livestock sector.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide expert guidance and opportunities for continuing education for professionals in Veterinary Sciences and Animal Husbandry.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide consultancy and specialists services to livestock owners, pet owners,&nbsp;semi-government, government, and associated agencies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"KHALSA COLLEGE OF VETERINARY & ANIMAL SCIENCES\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Punjab\",\"city\":\"Amritsar\",\"degree\":\"B.V.Sc. AH\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Boys Hostel\r\n	<p>The College provides on Campus accommodation for outstation students. There are seven blocks - three for boys viz. Nabha, Faridkot, and Hargobind. It provides accommodation for 400 students. Each hostel is provided with spacious rooms, adequate storage areas, hygienic mess, a dining hall, a reading room with newspapers, periodicals and magazines, a TV set etc. Strict discipline is maintained in the hostel. The right of admission to the hostel is reserved with the Hostel Management Body functional under the Principal.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Hostel\r\n	<p>The College provides on Campus accommodation for outstation students. . The separate Girls Hostel is situated at Green Avenue having the capacity of 100 students. Each hostel is provided with spacious rooms, adequate storage areas, hygienic mess, a dining hall, a reading room with newspapers, periodicals and magazines, a TV set etc. Strict discipline is maintained in the hostel. The right of admission to the hostel is reserved with the Hostel Management Body functional under the Principal.Gym</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The college has Gym facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Library\r\n	<p>The college has a spacious library having more than 2000 books on various disciplines of Veterinary &amp; Animal Sciences for students. Various national and international journals are also available. The spacious reading area lends a calm and comfortable atmosphere for students and faculty members to pursue excellence in academics.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sports\r\n	<p>The Collge has a volley ball court, badminton court, basket ball court and ground for cricket and football for students and staff.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria\r\n	<p>The college has a canteen facility for staff and students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium\r\n	<p>Large college auditorium is available ideally suited to hold Conferences and Exhibitions. It is a central hub of all types of academic, curricular, co-curricular activities including social events.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Hospital\r\n	<p>The college has health center with first aid facility for the students.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>IT Infrastructure\r\n	<p>The College has a computer science laboratory with thin-client networking, where PCs are interconnected to internet through Broadband. The laboratory is equipped with all types of modern technological facilities and is able to provide advanced training to students on various aspects of computer applications.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratorie\r\n	<p>the department has a well-equipped laboratory for conducting practical classes of B.V.Sc. &amp; A.H. students. These laboratories are designed as per new guidelines of VCI. Glassware, instruments and other necessary facilities are provided to the student to understand the essence of the theory A well equipped veterinary investigation laboratory is available in the college. The lab provides a full range of animal disease diagnostic services to veterinarians, livestock producers and pet owners in and around Amritsar.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Room\r\n	<p>The college has guest house/waiting room facilities for visiting faculty and student family members.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '', '', '', '2022-03-16 16:33:19', '2022-03-16 16:41:19'),
(70, 'AVADH INSTITUTE OF MEDICAL TECHNOLOGY & HOSPITAL', NULL, 'avadh-institute-of-medical-technology--hospital', '', NULL, 33, 796, '164786374176.png', '164786374197.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '', '2010', '', '', '<p>Avadh Institute of Medical Technologies and Hospital was formally established in December, 2004. It is located near village Paikramau, Kursi Road, Lucknow in Uttar Pradesh (226007), India. It is governed by AL-MILLAT foundation trust. Our students acquire generic set of skills with the help of the top-notch faculty, latest technology and learning tools at their disposal. Our students are trained with world class competency and cutting edge proficiency to face the professional world with confidence.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>VISION</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To be a center of excellence in teaching, training, research, innovation and medical care facilities by attracting best talents, brains and man power for the benefit of the society as a whole.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>MISSION</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our mission is to curate, create and disseminate knowledge and academic excellence so as to produce graduates and postgraduates who are fully prepared to achieve highest level of personal and professional distinction.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>DEPARTMENT</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At&nbsp;<strong>Avadh Institute of Medical Technologies and Hospital</strong>, you have an opportunity to discover what inspires you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NURSING&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PHARMACY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PARAMEDICAL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"AVADH INSTITUTE OF MEDICAL TECHNOLOGY & HOSPITAL\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Lucknow\",\"degree\":\"B. Pharma,D. Pharma,GNM,ANM\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p><strong>CAMPUS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sprawling campus spread over 15 acres of land with fully ventilated building and open area for garden and sports activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The campus is Wi-Fi enabled.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CLASS ROOMS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The class rooms are equipped with high tech facilities like technical learning tools (audio-visual aids) and high speed internet connectivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HOSTELS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our hostels are preferred residential option for the students. The college provides separate residential facility for boys and girls that includes food, laundry and recreational facilities. The hostel has full time residential wardens and caretakers to look after the residential logistics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AUDITORIUM</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students have a very fascinating fully air-conditioned, state-of-the-art auditorium and seminar rooms equipped with the latest audio visual facilities for seminars, guest lectures, conferences and presentations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LABS AND WORKSHOPS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has well-furnished and spacious laboratories with all experimental set up.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nursing and Fundamental lab.</li>\r\n	<li>Nutrition and Community lab.</li>\r\n	<li>Anatomy and Physiology lab.</li>\r\n	<li>Bio-Chemistry, Pathology and Microbiology lab.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CANTEEN/CAFETERIA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students have access to healthy and hygienic food at subsidized rates within the college campus. Regular inspection for quality check is conducted by the quality commitment team to keep check on the nutritional value and quality of food served. The ambience of the canteen makes the learning experience more enjoyable and relaxing, hence becomes the hub for out-of-class discussions and exchange of information. The students get a home away from home within the premises of the college.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HOSPITAL</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A 100 bedded hospital provides hands-on training to the trainees. The students have an advantage of full time medical assistance for their routine health issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPORTS AND WELLNESS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in playing hard and working harder. We make our students ready for the challenges ahead through mental and physical fitness. Our academics is complemented by competitive athletics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LIBRARY FACILITY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our students have an access to our central library which is well stocked with large number of books and journals and is fully-computerized. The vital key for developing ones individual potentiality is certainly access to information therefore the library has subscribed newspapers, periodicals and journals (both national and international) so as to keep our students well informed and well-read.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMPUTER LABS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College has a well-furnished computer lab with modern equipped terminals and loaded with high-end softwares pertaining to the courses. There is 24 hours power backup. The campus is Wi-Fi enabled.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TRANSPORT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide well maintained buses for pick and drop of our students and staff that are managed by our courteous and efficient staff. All the transport related services are under the supervision of the transport officer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BIOMETRIC ATTENDANCE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fingerprint based attendance software for students attendance. Auto data download feature in the machine. SMS notification feature to update parents.</p>', '3.8', '', '', '', '2022-03-21 16:55:41', '2022-03-21 17:12:11'),
(71, 'ITS DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'its-dental-college-', '', NULL, 33, 776, '164794550567.png', '164794550590.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '', '', '2006', '', '', '<p>ITS - The Education Group is the fastest growing educational group in Northern India. Since its inception in 1995 the ITS Group has consistently built on its reputation as a premier group of professional institutions of Management, IT, Engineering, Dental Sciences, Paramedical Sciences and Pharmacy. True to its motto &ldquo; In Service For A Healthy Nation &ldquo; , the ITS Dental College, Hospital &amp; Research Centre focuses on both the rural and urban population by providing free transport, medicines and heavily subsidized treatment to the patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The group utilizes the skills and experience of outstanding faculty, staff and students who share the passion in creating an institution known for its excellence and integrity. Blending tradition with neo realities, the ITS Group lays emphasis on four cardinal tenets-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 1. Academic Rigor&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 2. Advanced Technology&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 3. Practical / Clinical Application</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 4. Ethical Standards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THE COLLEGE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ITS Dental College, Hospital &amp; Research Centre is situated in an Institutional Area (Knowledge Park III) of Greater Noida, U.P. This is a District Head Quarter about 25 km. from New Delhi and is located in the National Capital Region (NCR). The accessibility of the College by means of public and private transport is extremely good. The populated areas around the college provide the clinical material so vital for training in life sciences. The infrastructure is more than sufficient to fulfill the academic, administrative and residential requirements of the students and faculty and is at par with the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college is a self financed institution, recognized by Dental Council of India, Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare and is affiliated to Ch. Charan Singh University, Meerut. The College is offering a five year Bachelor of Dental Surgery (B.D.S) with an intake of 100 students per batch and three year Master of Dental Surgery (M.D.S) Programme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AIMS &amp; OBJECTIVES</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The aim and objective of ITS Dental College, Hospital &amp; Research Centre, Greater Noida is to prepare a socially acceptable dentist with adequate knowledge and necessary skills for appropriate dental practice including prevention, diagnosis and treatment of dental and orofacial diseases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this institute the students are encouraged to participate in &quot;Group Discussions&quot; and &quot;Seminars&quot; to help them develop expression, character and personality and other qualities essential for a dental graduate to serve the community and nation effectively.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"ITS DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Gautam Buddha Nagar\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '', '4.7', '', '', '', '2022-03-22 14:43:04', '2022-03-22 15:42:35'),
(72, 'BABU BANARASI DAS UNIVERSITY', NULL, 'babu-banarasi-das-university', '', NULL, 33, 796, '164794635834.png', '164794635858.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', 'OVER 30', '2010', '', '', '<p><strong>Babu Banarasi Das University, Lucknow</strong>&nbsp;is a Private University located in the capital city of Lucknow of the state Uttar Pradesh. The Institute was established in 2010 by Akhilesh Das. BBD University is fully recognized by the AICTE, New Delhi and also got NAAC accreditation. The University is envisioned to transform the way people think by teaching them problem-solving, leadership and teamwork skills, and the value of commitment to quality, ethical behavior, and respect for others. The University offers&nbsp;<a href=\"https://collegedunia.com/university/25923-babu-banarasi-das-university-bbdu-lucknow/courses-fees\" target=\"_blank\">Undergraduate, Postgraduate, Ph.D., integrated MBA and Certification level courses</a>&nbsp;in streams like Engineering, Management, Computer Applications, Pharmacy, Hotel Management, Architecture, Dental Science, Applied Sciences, Humanities, Social studies, Legal Studies, and Education.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"BABU BANARASI DAS UNIVERSITY\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Lucknow\",\"degree\":\"BDS,B. Pharma\",\"exam\":\"Neet,NEET\"}', '', '3.6', '', '', '', '2022-03-22 15:47:45', '2022-03-22 16:16:35'),
(73, 'Sri Venkateshwaraa Medical College Hospital & Research Centre', NULL, 'sri-venkateshwaraa-medical-college-hospital--research-centre', '', NULL, 27, 588, '165817155668.jpg', '165817155688.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30 Acres', '459', '2008', '', '145', '<p><strong>Sri Venkateshwaraa Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre</strong>&nbsp;is promoted by Ramachandra Educational Trust, Chennai. The Chairman Shri. B. Ramachandran is a successful educationalist and a visionary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Towards a Healthier Society.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We at Sri Venkateshwaraa Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Centre on the Puducherry-Villupuram National Highway are committed to creating a healthier society. Towards this end, we provide one of the best tertiary care services in the state. Our holistic approach to healthcare begins with primary care and extends to specialized treatments. We ensure multi disciplinary approach and patient centric care, which are essential for compassionate care. At SVMC every patient is guaranteed the best medical, diagnostic and surgical services. Our services reach over 5,00,000 outpatients and 40,000 inpatients a year.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Sri Venkateshwaraa Medical College Hospital & Research Centre\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Pondicherry\",\"city\":\"Pondicherry\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '5', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-07-19 00:12:36', '2022-07-19 00:12:36'),
(74, 'Sri Manakula Vinayagar Medical College', NULL, 'sri-manakula-vinayagar-medical-college', '', NULL, 27, 588, '165823962385.jpg', '165823962375.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '39 Acres', '131+', '2006', '', '140', '<p>Sri Manakula Vinayagar Group of Institutions offer courses in Medicine, Engineering, Nursing, Polytechnic and Education offering 52 courses. Our campus spread across 225 acres of land with built up area of more than 25 Lakhs square feet to grown it. We have more than 12500 students, 2500 employees, 150 buses, hostel accommodation for 2000 students and more than 200 staff quarters.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>University Gold medals and 9 out of 10 University ranks continuously from the inception</li>\r\n		<li>Conducted over 6000 surgeries in a year</li>\r\n		<li>The Nephrology department performs more than 1100 cycles of dialysis per month for renal failure patients</li>\r\n		<li>12 Ultra-Modern operation theaters with laminar flow</li>\r\n		<li>900 bedded ultra-modern tertiary care and super specialty hospital</li>\r\n		<li>In 2015, South India Medical students conference held in Sri Manakula Vinayagar Medical College and Hospital&rsquo;s central auditorium conducted by the students attracted over 500 Professionals, Faculties and Students</li>\r\n		<li>75 students were awarded prizes for winning various national and International competitions in the year 2014-2015</li>\r\n		<li>475 Seminars / Workshops were organized by the institute in the last five years</li>\r\n		<li>​17 Books were published by the faculty of SMVMCH in last 5 years</li>\r\n		<li>In first half of this decade, faculties have submitted 552 research papers</li>\r\n		<li>National level events of 12 were organized in the year 2014-2015</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Sri Manakula Vinayagar Medical College\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Pondicherry\",\"city\":\"Pondicherry\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h2>Hospital Facilities</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sri Manakula Vinayagar Medical College and Hospital is an Ultramodern, multi-speciality tertiary care hospital with medical research facilities. The hospital has an inpatient capacity of more than 900 beds, exclusive of 100 critical care beds in different specialties. As tertiary care and super specialty hospital, the services are complemented with a day care center, outpatient facilities and an exclusive center for health checkups . With over 300 doctors therein always an experienced specialist on hand to treat.Preventive health is the need of the hour for health conscious people. With this in mind, we have designed different specific Health Check-up packages ranging from basic pre-employment check-up to a comprehensive medical check-up.(These can be further tailor-made and cost-customized to suit various requirements. The hospital&rsquo;s catering department serves nutritious vegetarian food under the guidance of qualified dieticians. An in-house pharmacy provides all essential medicines, medical an allied services to the patients, thus ensuring total control over the quality of drugs administered to patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The hospital has computerized all admissions, billing and discharge procedures to save time.</p>', '5', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-07-19 19:07:03', '2022-07-19 19:07:03'),
(75, 'Chettinad Academy of Research and Education', NULL, 'chettinad-academy-of-research-and-education-2', '', NULL, 31, 693, '165832647496.jpg', '165832647484.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'NMC', '', '95 Acres', '220', '2006', '', '778', '<p><strong>Chettinad Hospital and Research Institute (CHRI), Kelambakkam</strong>&nbsp;was established in the year 2006. The campus spreads over 95 acres of land. CHRI is a constituent college of the Chettinad Academy of Research and Education (CARE). The college offers undergraduate (MBBS), postgraduate (MD, MS, PGD) and super speciality courses in various areas. The institute has secured 49th rank in the Medical category in NIRF 2021 Ranking.&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Chettinad Academy of Research and Education\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '5', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-07-20 19:14:34', '2022-07-20 19:14:34'),
(76, 'KARPAGA VINAYAGA INSTITUTE OF MEDICAL SCIENCES (KIMS)', NULL, 'karpaga-vinayaga-institute-of-medical-sciences-kims', '', NULL, 31, 693, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><em><strong>Karpaga Vinayaga Educational Group (2001) caters to various education disciplines like Medicine, Dentistry, Engineering, Nursing and Allied Health Sciences.&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The group comprises Karpaga Vinayaga College of&nbsp;Engineering and Technology, Karpaga Vinayaga Institute of Dental Sciences, Karpaga Vinayaga Institute of Medical Sciences, Karpaga Vinayaga College of Nursing in a sprawling serene campus away from the hustle and bustle of the city but still in close proximity to the scene. All institutions boast of dedicated and well-qualified faculty members, Infrastructure and students from all over India and other countries. Excellent facilities and amenities and above all quality education is provided to cater to the needs of this competitive field.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"KARPAGA VINAYAGA INSTITUTE OF MEDICAL SCIENCES (KIMS)\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-07-23 18:43:02', '2022-07-23 18:43:02'),
(77, 'Panimalar Medical College Hospital & Research Institute', NULL, 'panimalar-medical-college-hospital--research-institute', '', NULL, 31, 722, '165875258676.jpg', '165875258680.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '45.745 acres', '459', '2005', '', '', '<p>Panimalar Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Institute is a Christian Minority Institution of Higher Education established and governed by the &ldquo;Jaisakthi Educational Trust&rdquo;, Chennai. Jaisakthi Educational Trust aims at imparting quality engineering, medical, nursing and other health professions education for the aspiring youth. The college is located at Varardharajapuram near Poonamallee, Chennai and is well connected by road covering Chennai, Kancheepuram and Thiruvallur districts. The Jaisakthi Educational Trust started Panimalar Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Institute in the year 2017 in accordance with the general policy of the Government of Tamilnadu. The College is well-equipped with the state of the art infrastructure, technology-enabled smart classrooms, advanced laboratories and continually focuses on teaching, clinical practice, and research.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This sprawling campus provides a holistic education in an ambiance that makes no compromise on discipline, dedication, and commitment. It strives to inculcate the spirit of learning in the campus offering state of the art facilities and learning environment to the students. The college ensures that the students who pass out of the college, turn out to be academically brilliant, morally upright, and empowered individuals.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Panimalar Medical College Hospital & Research Institute\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Pudukkottai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p>The infrastructure and facility available on campus are the very best&rdquo; The Panimalar Medical College Hospital &amp; Research Institute campus spreads over 50 acres in a spacious, noise free, clean, green zone and serene atmosphere ideally suited for technical education. The infrastructure and facilities available on campus are the very best. It is a wholly self-contained campus containing everything that students on campus would ever require.</p>', '', '', '', '', '2022-07-25 17:36:26', '2022-07-25 19:11:29'),
(78, 'Karpaga Vinayaga Institute of Medical Sciences & Research Institute', NULL, 'karpaga-vinayaga-institute-of-medical-sciences--research-institute', '', NULL, 31, 712, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Karpaga Vinayaga Institute of Medical Sciences & Research Institute\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Mayiladuthurai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-07-29 15:28:37', '2022-07-29 15:28:37'),
(79, 'Dr. B.R. Ambedkar Medical College - [BRAMC], Bangalore', NULL, 'dr-br-ambedkar-medical-college--bramc-bangalore', '', 'india', 17, 362, '166193700326.jpg', '166193700364.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '', '83', '1981', '31.30 Lakhs', '587', '<p>Dr. B.R.Ambedkar Medical College is a private college, established in 1981 by an education trust known as Ananda Social and Education Trust. The college is affiliated with Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sciences and approved by the Medical Council of India. It provides top quality medical education internationally and is evolving towards a global knowledge of Medicine, Pharmacy, Paramedics etc.</p>', 1, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Dr. B.R. Ambedkar Medical College - [BRAMC], Bangalore\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Karnataka\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p>Dr. BR Ambedkar Medical College offers varied infrastructure and facilities for the students and faculty such as a library with a collection of books and journals, hostels, sports, mess, transport facilities, etc. Other facilities like Wi-Fi, ATM facilities, etc are also available for the students and faculty.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Hostel</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Library</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cafeteria and Mess</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sports:&nbsp;BRAMC &nbsp;provides both indoor and outdoor games facilities like badminton, table tennis, football, swimming pool, lawn tennis, etc.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Transport Facilities</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Boys Hostel</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Girls Hostel</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Library</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sports</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cafeteria: There is a canteen and a Coffee shop in campus. The canteen provides hygienic multi-cuisine awesome food throughout the day.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Auditorium</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Medical/Hospital</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>IT Infrastructure</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Transport</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Alumni Associations</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Banks Facilities:&nbsp; An ATM is conveniently located on the campus</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '', '', '', '2022-08-31 13:37:32', '2023-02-20 17:44:37'),
(80, 'Career Institute of Dental Sciences & Hospital, Lucknow', NULL, 'career-institute-of-dental-sciences--hospital-lucknow', '', NULL, 33, 796, '166221081992.jpg', '166221081914.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '40 acres', '215', '2012', '', '867', '<p><strong>Career Post Graduate Institute of Dental Sciences &amp; Hospital</strong>&nbsp;is situated in the lush green belt of Lucknow, on Sitapur-Hardoi Bypass Road in the vicinity of I.I.M. It is spread over an area of 40 acres of land having all necessary facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Chief Founder Trustee Mrs. Haseena Azmat and Mr. Azmat Ali Founder trustee have been a source of inspiration in Implementing and establishing this institution side by side and separately to give benefit to the upcoming student. Our Institute has various eminent &amp; competent faculties. Dr. Pradyumna Misra is our Principal and is also Head of Department, Conservative Dentistry &amp; Endodontic.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Career Institute of Dental Sciences & Hospital, Lucknow\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Lucknow\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p><strong>The Institute has following other modern facilities e.g.</strong><br />\r\nSeparate Hostels for boys &amp; Girls.<br />\r\nLuxury Buses for transportation of students.<br />\r\nState of Art Mess and canteen facility in the campus.<br />\r\nWell-equipped college Library with Internet facility.<br />\r\nFacility for indoor and outdoor games.Educational tours and medical camps conducted from time to time for benefit of the students.<br />\r\nBuses for transportation of students and patients.</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2022-09-03 18:13:39', '2022-09-03 18:13:48');
