(81, 'Chandra Dental College & Hospital, safedabad', NULL, 'chandra-dental-college--hospital-safedabad', '', NULL, 33, 821, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '30 Acres', '200', '2003', '', '548', '<p>Chandra Dental College &amp; Hospital is running successfully on Lucknow - Ayodhya National Highway. It has affiliated with Atal Bihari Vajpayee Medical University, Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh. It is also recognized by the Dental Council of India(DCI) and the Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare, Government of India, New Delhi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chandra Dental College &amp; Hospital is functioning since 2003. It is affiliated with Dr Ram Manohar Lohia Avadh University, Faizabad. It is also approved by the Dental Council of Uttar Pradesh and India, and the Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare, Government of India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The College is actively involved in quality teaching and research practices in oral health care which makes it a centre of excellence for providing world-class education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college is well equipped with a state-of-art dental clinical setup and a modern and majestic infrastructure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has well-established simulated pre-clinical and research labs. The air-conditioned central library opens during college hours. An Audio-visual room with multi-media facilities adds academic interest for students. Besides this, all classrooms have Overhead projectors, Slide projectors, PA systems and other online information systems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A separate hostel for girls and boys situated in a serene environment with round-the-clock Wi-Fi connectivity and uninterrupted power supply and water supply makes it conducive for concentrated studies. There is an indoor sports room and outdoor ground that gives a boost for athletic development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The large number of patients visiting OPD of dental college is its major strength. The college has a super speciality clinical setting which attracts both rural as well as the urban population. The college has well equipped mobile dental van that caters to the needs of the underprivileged.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Chandra Dental College & Hospital, safedabad\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Varanasi\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p><strong>Research</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The institution has facilities for research activities.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Well Equipped Lab</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute has state of the art labs for Bio -chemistry, Physiology, Dental material, Anatomy, Pharmacology, Microbiology, Pathology, Pre-clinical Conservative, and Radiology equipped with modern instruments and machines. Under the supreme guidance of highly qualified faculty members and well trained lab technicians, students learn implementation of their theoretical knowledge practically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Library</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The library has a meticulously chosen selection of more than 3000 books of Indian and foreign origin. Books on Medical, dental, Pharmacology, Computers, medical / Dental Information Systems and other reading materials are available in the library for ready reference and issue.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>The library provides the following student support services:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Book Lending Services</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Reference and Information Services</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Reprographic services</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Reading Room facility</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>National and International Database</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hostel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The residential complex accommodates both the Boys and Girls hostel separately. Spacious and well-furnished rooms (AC &amp; Non AC) with adequate furniture provides the students with a perfect, hassle-free stay. Rooms are available on a single and twin-sharing basis in both hostels. All necessary arrangements have been made for the safety, security and privacy of the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AC Gym</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has Air conditioned gym with all the modern equipment. An 8-hourly certified instructor provides all health care tips and guidance to all gym users. Different time slots are marked for boys and girls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transportation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has its own transportation facility with 4 college buses, each has been divided into different areas of Lucknow so that commuting is easy for students and staff of the college</p>', '5', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Anti Ragging</li>\r\n	<li>Counselling Services</li>\r\n	<li>Healthcare Services</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel(Male and Female)</li>\r\n	<li>Query</li>\r\n	<li>Report</li>\r\n	<li>Technical Issues</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '2022-09-05 14:25:38', '2022-09-05 15:10:46'),
(82, 'DJ College Of Dental Sciences & Research', NULL, 'dj-college-of-dental-sciences--research', '', NULL, 33, 876, '166237531919.jpg', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '6.8 Acres', '230', '1999', '', '', '<p>The core qualities that makes Divya Jyoti College of Dental Sciences stand apart from other dental colleges is our commitment to a comprehensive education that strikes a balance between excellence in contemporary dental education, scientific judgment and emotional intelligence &ndash; that indefinable extra factor that is expected in a doctor who is ethical, clinically proficient, empathetic, and a responsible citizen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a center for academic and clinical excellence where emphasis is laid on the importance of didactic coursework, pre-clinical training, clinical experience, and practice management that prepares the students to enter the workforce as confident and globally competitive clinicians.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"DJ College Of Dental Sciences & Research\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Modinagar\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Central Library</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>College Events</li>\r\n	<li>Sports</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>Campus &amp; Hostel</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-09-05 15:55:19', '2022-09-05 15:55:19'),
(83, 'Dental College Azamgarh', NULL, 'dental-college-azamgarh', '', NULL, 33, 755, '166237719161.jpg', '166237719183.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '30 Acres', '250', '1977', '16,32,000', '1500', '<p>Dental College Azamgarh is one of the reputed&nbsp;Private Dental College in Uttar Pradesh. The college was founded in the year 2005-06.&nbsp;The college was established to fortify the weakest section of the Nation, i.e. Rural population. Azamgarh Dental College&nbsp;was started to serve students with the best dental care and&nbsp;Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery. Now the college has become synonymous with one of the&nbsp;Best Dental Colleges in&nbsp;Uttar Pradesh<strong>.</strong></p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Dental College Azamgarh\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Azamgarh\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2022-09-05 16:26:31', '2022-09-05 16:49:18'),
(84, 'ANIL NEERUKONDA INSTITUTE OF DENTAL SCIENCES', NULL, 'anil-neerukonda-institute-of-dental-sciences', '', NULL, 2, 97, '166244548241.jpg', '166244548222.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '30 Acres', '150', '', '', '2500+', '<p><strong>Vision</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To raise the bar for dental education by fostering leadership values and delivering highly competent training.</li>\r\n	<li>To produce excellent, medically competent dental professionals by offering a solid clinical and biotechnical education through a faculty that is highly qualified and experienced.</li>\r\n	<li>to offer a top-notch academic environment and infrastructure that supports the advanced study.</li>\r\n	<li>being a centre of excellence for patient care, dental research, and education.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Creating a world-class academic dental school that fosters excellence in oral health care, research, dental education, and community service would help the population&#39;s general health.</li>\r\n	<li>To offer the society comprehensive patient care at a reasonable price.</li>\r\n	<li>to train qualified, experienced faculty in several areas of oral health care.</li>\r\n	<li>to instil in the institution&#39;s students a high level of professional competence.</li>\r\n	<li>To achieve this in a setting that is ethical and encouraging, compatible with our core values of quality, service, fairness, compassion, and effective communication, and in line with the strategic plan of the Anil Neerukonda Educational Society.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Goals</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To become one of India&#39;s top dental schools.</li>\r\n	<li>To create an academic environment that is stimulating and to establish ANIDS as a centre of excellence in order to meaningfully contribute to our national goal of &quot;Health for all.&quot;</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"ANIL NEERUKONDA INSTITUTE OF DENTAL SCIENCES\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Andhra Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Visakhapatnam\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Classrooms</li>\r\n	<li>Seminar Halls</li>\r\n	<li>Examination Cell</li>\r\n	<li>Sports &amp; Cultural Activities</li>\r\n	<li>ICT Enabled</li>\r\n	<li>Simulation Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Gender Equity</li>\r\n	<li>Renewable Energy</li>\r\n	<li>Water Conservations</li>\r\n	<li>Green Campus</li>\r\n	<li>Divyangjan</li>\r\n	<li>Equipments</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', '', '', '2022-09-06 11:24:42', '2022-09-06 11:26:02'),
(85, 'CKS TEJA INSTITUTE OF DENTAL SCIENCES AND RESEARCH', NULL, 'cks-teja-institute-of-dental-sciences-and-research', '', NULL, 2, 873, '166244944161.jpg', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '1999', '20,75,700', '2500+', '<p>A CKS Theja Institute of Dental Sciences and Research, A.P is quite proud of our top-notch institution, which is unmatched in Andhra Pradesh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For clinical clients, students, and their parents who appreciate our welcoming, student-supportive learning atmosphere, great smiles start here. They provide a state-of-the art academic, research, and clinical environment for aspiring dental surgeons in the temple town of Tirupathi, one of India&#39;s most revered and clean cities.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"CKS TEJA INSTITUTE OF DENTAL SCIENCES AND RESEARCH\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Andhra Pradesh\",\"city\":\"Tirupati\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<h2>LABORATORIES</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The institute has hitech labs equipped with modern instruments &amp; machines. Various labs, like Dental Materials, Pre Clinical Conservative, Pre Clinical Prosthetics, Dental Anatomy, Oral Pathology etc. are available for effective learning, to learn and under stand the disease process at a micro level, and also to improve the manual skills before they treat the patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>CENTRAL&nbsp;LIBRARY</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The library is spread over an area of more than 10,000 sft with seperate UG&amp;PG reading areas, staff reading area, journal section, xerox facility, and E-Library facility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>LECTURE&nbsp;THEATRE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Lecture theatre well ventilated and equipped with LCD and OHP projectors and audio-visual equipment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>HOSTELS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>CKS Teja Institute of Dental College has separate hostels for boys and girls with well furnished rooms and modern amenities. The overall atmosphere is very conducive for the students to concentrate on their studies. We ensure that students dwell in a healthy environment that helps them to grow and learn without any obstacles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>COLLEGE&nbsp;OPD</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>CKS Teja Institute of Dental College has separate Out Patient Department (OPD) for daily OPD of patients. Students are exposed to a wide variety of cases to improve their academic and clinical skills. The OPD is fully functional with state of the art equipments for diagnosis &amp; treatment.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />', '4.9', '', '', '', '2022-09-06 12:30:41', '2022-09-06 12:32:20'),
(86, 'Meenakshi Ammal Dental College & Hospital Chennai', NULL, 'meenakshi-ammal-dental-college--hospital-chennai', '', NULL, 31, 693, '166245107653.jpg', '166245107684.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '5 acres', '', '2004', '', '2500+', '<p>This dental institution, which occupies a vast 5 acres in Chennai, the state&#39;s capital, is home to many smart and imaginative individuals. The educators foster the students effectively in the clinical, academic, and research parts of dentistry by giving them individualised attention.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Meenakshi Ammal Dental College & Hospital Chennai\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>These&nbsp;are&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chennai,&nbsp;Meenakshi&nbsp;Ammal&nbsp;Dental&nbsp;College&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Hospital.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students&nbsp;who&nbsp;are&nbsp;enrolled&nbsp;in&nbsp;or&nbsp;have&nbsp;already&nbsp;started&nbsp;attending&nbsp;MADCH&nbsp;Chennai&nbsp;are&nbsp;provided&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;amenities:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a name=\"_Hlk113288885\">Medical</a></li>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Sport</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-09-06 12:57:56', '2022-09-06 12:57:56'),
(87, 'SAVEETHA DENTAL COLLEGE IN CHENNAI', NULL, 'saveetha-dental-college-in-chennai', '', NULL, 31, 693, '166245909898.jpg', '166245909819.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '30 Acres', '220', '', '', '250', '<p>One&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;premier&nbsp;universities&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world,&nbsp;Saveetha&nbsp;Dental&nbsp;College&nbsp;in&nbsp;Chennai,&nbsp;Tamil&nbsp;Nadu,&nbsp;India,&nbsp;offers&nbsp;a&nbsp;distinctive&nbsp;curriculum&nbsp;that&nbsp;brilliantly&nbsp;blends&nbsp;the&nbsp;best&nbsp;techniques&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;east&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;west.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our&nbsp;unwavering&nbsp;enthusiasm&nbsp;has&nbsp;enabled&nbsp;us&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;our&nbsp;students&nbsp;with&nbsp;unparalleled&nbsp;training&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;clinical,&nbsp;academic,&nbsp;and&nbsp;research&nbsp;areas.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SAVEETHA DENTAL COLLEGE IN CHENNAI\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p>The following amenities are provided to potential or current students at Chennai Dental College by Saveetha Dental College Chennai: -</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Medical</li>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Sports</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Centre of Community Medicine</p>', '4.8', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-09-06 15:11:38', '2022-09-06 15:11:38'),
(88, 'SRI BALAJI DENTAL COLLEGE, NARAYANAPURAM, CHENNAI', NULL, 'sri-balaji-dental-college-narayanapuram-chennai', '', NULL, 31, 693, '166246101812.jpg', '166246101834.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '1,75,000 sft.', '40', '1989', '', '200', '<p>The&nbsp;college&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Bharath&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;of&nbsp;Higher&nbsp;Education&nbsp;and&nbsp;Research&nbsp;(BIHER)&nbsp;aspires&nbsp;to&nbsp;and&nbsp;works&nbsp;hard&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;a&nbsp;top-notch&nbsp;academic&nbsp;and&nbsp;research&nbsp;environment&nbsp;for&nbsp;students&nbsp;and&nbsp;faculty&nbsp;members&nbsp;to&nbsp;inherit&nbsp;professional&nbsp;competence,&nbsp;human&nbsp;dignity,&nbsp;and&nbsp;values&nbsp;to&nbsp;serve&nbsp;society&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;whole.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SRI BALAJI DENTAL COLLEGE, NARAYANAPURAM, CHENNAI\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The&nbsp;following&nbsp;are&nbsp;amenities&nbsp;provided&nbsp;by&nbsp;Sree&nbsp;Balaji&nbsp;Dental&nbsp;College&nbsp;Chennai&nbsp;for&nbsp;students&nbsp;who&nbsp;are&nbsp;considering&nbsp;enrolling&nbsp;there&nbsp;or&nbsp;who&nbsp;are&nbsp;already&nbsp;enrolled&nbsp;there:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Sport</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', '2022-09-06 15:43:38', '2022-09-06 15:44:44'),
(89, 'THAI MOOGAMBIGAI DENTAL COLLEGE & HOSPITAL Chennai', NULL, 'thai-moogambigai-dental-college--hospital-chennai', '', NULL, 31, 693, '166246485985.jpg', '166246485920.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Thai Moogambigai Dental College and Hospital (TMDCH) is one of the leading dental colleges in Chennai and a constituent unit of Dr. M.G.R. Educational and Research Institute, Deemed University. TMDCH is an ISO certified premium dental institution accredited with&nbsp;<strong>NAAC &lsquo;A&rsquo; grade</strong>&nbsp;(Score - 3.31 out of 4). TMDCH is a pioneer in the field of dental education and its inception dates back to 1991.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college is recognized by Dental Council of India and Government of India, Ministry of Health &amp; Family Welfare, New Delhi. The institution acquired its deemed status in 2003 and became a constituent unit of Dr MGR Educational and Research Institute University, as per the order by University Grants Commission, New Delhi and the Union Ministry of Human Resource and Development, Government of India. Started initially as an undergraduate institution with 100 seats, it has now grown into a full-fledged Post-graduate research institute. Both BDS and MDS courses are offered with the following specialities - Orthodontics, Periodontics, Oral &amp; Maxillofacial Surgery, Prosthodontics, Conservative Dentistry, Oral Medicine, Pedodontics and Oral Pathology.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"THAI MOOGAMBIGAI DENTAL COLLEGE & HOSPITAL Chennai\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The following are facilities provided by Thai Moogambigai Dental College Chennai for students who are considering attending or are already enrolled there:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Transport</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Security</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Fire Extinguisher</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Play ground</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Parking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Water treatment plant</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. Power backup</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Surveillance Camera</p>', '4.8', '', '', '', '2022-09-06 16:47:39', '2022-09-06 16:51:04'),
(90, 'SRI RAMACHANDRA DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'sri-ramachandra-dental-college', '', NULL, 31, 693, '166246641018.jpg', '166246641015.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '2,29,000 sq.ft', '200', '1995', '', '1200', '<p>Sri Ramachandra Dental College and Hospital was started in 1995 as a constituent college of Sri Ramachandra Institute of Higher Education and Research. &nbsp;Utilising a floor space of 2,29,000 sq.ft, the college has 330 well equipped dental chairs to fulfill the needs of the Undergraduates and Postgraduates in every branch of dentistry. There are specially designed laboratories and teaching facilities such as lecture halls,&nbsp;auditoria and departmental seminar rooms and departmental libraries which make this a well recognised institution in the country. Advanced diagnostic equipment such as Orthopantomographs, Cephalostats and maxillofacial and dental radiography have been included.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the state-of-the-art designated dental operation theatres, the vast diagnostic facilities, that are available at the medical centre are also readily accessible for the students and faculty of the dental college. Several hundred patients who visit the dental college and hospital every day appreciate the comprehensive care provided. Integrated for the BDS course is being introduced.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The B.D.S. Course offered is recognised by the Dental Council of India and the Dental Councils of&nbsp;Malaysia and Sri Lanka. Among the academic collaborations entered into by the college those with the Kyushu Dental College, Japan, are notable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SRI RAMACHANDRA DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"693\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The&nbsp;following&nbsp;amenities&nbsp;are&nbsp;provided&nbsp;to&nbsp;prospective&nbsp;and&nbsp;current&nbsp;students&nbsp;at&nbsp;Sri&nbsp;Ramachandra&nbsp;Dental&nbsp;College:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outstanding&nbsp;Library</li>\r\n	<li>a&nbsp;satellite&nbsp;facility</li>\r\n	<li>exemplary&nbsp;service</li>\r\n	<li>a&nbsp;cutting-edge&nbsp;ceramic&nbsp;and&nbsp;casting&nbsp;studio&nbsp;with&nbsp;imported&nbsp;gear</li>\r\n	<li>sophisticated&nbsp;machinery&nbsp;and&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;to&nbsp;begin&nbsp;post-graduate&nbsp;courses</li>\r\n	<li>Tobacco-Free&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Ragging-Free&nbsp;Campus</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', '2022-09-06 17:13:30', '2022-09-06 17:21:22'),
(91, 'CSI COLLEGE OF DENTAL SCIENCES AND RESEARCH', NULL, 'csi-college-of-dental-sciences-and-research', '', NULL, 31, 711, '166254126525.jpg', '166254126519.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'DCI', '', '30 Acres', '459', '2007', '1,30,000', '1800', '<p>One of the renowned private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is the CSI College of Dental Sciences and Research in Madurai. The college was established in 2007&ndash;2008 and is often known as CSI Dental College Madurai. The college is a part of Chennai&#39;s Tamil Nadu Dr. M.G.R. Medical University. It has the Government of India&#39;s Dental Council&#39;s approval.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"CSI COLLEGE OF DENTAL SCIENCES AND RESEARCH\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Madurai\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The following CSI College of Dental Sciences and Research amenities are available to students who are considering attending or are currently enrolled:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Medical</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Student Houses</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Library</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Scholarships</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hostel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Blood Bank</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Laboratory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ragging tobacco-free campus</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs