(92, 'JKKN DENTAL COLLEGE AND HOSPITAL', NULL, 'jkkn-dental-college-and-hospital', '', NULL, 31, 710, '166254731253.png', '166254731246.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '10 acres', '126', '1987', '', '400', '<p>One of the well-known private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is JKKN Dental College and Hospital Komarapalayam. The institution was established in 1987&ndash;88 and is often known as JKKN Dental College Komarapalayam. It is affiliated with the Tamil Nadu M.G.R.G.R. Medical University and has received government of India&#39;s Dental Council&#39;s approval.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"JKKN DENTAL COLLEGE AND HOSPITAL\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"710\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The following CSI College of Dental Sciences and Research amenities are available to students who are considering attending or are currently enrolled:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Library</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IT Infrastructure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hostel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Blood Bank</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Laboratory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Auditorium</p>', '', '', '', '', '2022-09-07 15:41:52', '2022-09-07 15:42:52'),
