(94, 'KSR DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'ksr-dental-college', '', NULL, 31, 731, '166262243629.jpg', '166262243640.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>A highly skilled faculty that conveys knowledge and develops students&#39; talents is a strength of the college. The Dental Council of India&#39;s prescribed curriculum is followed. The College has partnerships with Sree Gokulam Hospital in Salem and Government Hospital in Tiruchengode for clinical training in general surgery and medicine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"KSR DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"31\",\"city\":\"731\",\"degree\":\"BDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The following KSR Dental College amenities are available to students who are considering attending or are currently enrolled:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Library</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IT Infrastructure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hostel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Blood Bank</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Laboratory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Auditorium</p>', '', '', '', '', '2022-09-08 11:45:28', '2022-09-08 12:59:10'),
(95, 'MADHA DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'madha-dental-college', '', NULL, 31, 693, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '5 acres', '150', '2007', '', '1834', '<p>One of the renowned private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is Madha Dental College &amp; Hospital Kundrathur. Madha Dental College Kundrathur, often known as MDCH Kundrathur, was established in 2007&ndash;2008. The school is infamously referred to by its students as a Private Dental College Kundrathur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The college conducts regular camps and provides free services to the population of the villages, surrounding the Kundrathur area via its community Outreach program as part of the Public Health and Community Dentistry Department. The College publishes an annual journal, which during the year 2019 was released by the honourable President of the Dental Council of India, Dr Dibyantu Mazumdar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivering top-notch medical programmes with highly competent staff and cutting-edge facilities is Madha Dental College Kundrathur. The College is renowned for its five-year undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Faculty and Staff:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The faculty at this college is well-educated, well-trained, and equipped with contemporary technology. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for raising and maintaining the standards of medical education at the Madha Dental College &amp; Hospital Kundrathur in their capacity as faculty members of the organisation.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inappropriate variation in value-based approaches should be reduced</li>\r\n	<li>Pose a more logical and sensible attitude toward the problem. Taught.</li>\r\n	<li>to serve as the centre of attention for quality control, including audit</li>\r\n	<li>To draw attention to the 