(97, 'SRI VENKATESWARA DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'sri-venkateswara-dental-college-', '', NULL, 31, 693, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>One of the well-known private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is Sri Venkateswara Dental College &amp; Hospital in Chennai. The college was established in 2007&ndash;2008 and is generally known as SVDCH Chennai. The College is affiliated with Tamil Nadu Dr. M.G.R. Medical University in Chennai and has received government of India&#39;s Dental Council&#39;s approval. The College seeks to produce competent dental graduates with great skills and knowledge who can deliver the best medical treatment to society by offering high-quality education and advanced training to the students. The faculty at the college is renowned for their expertise and strong qualifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Faculty and Staff:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This college offers a solid mix of highly educated, well-trained, and technologically advanced faculty members. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for maintaining and raising the calibre of medical education at Sri Venkateswara Dental College Chennai as faculty members. The following policies, which are applicable, are followed by all campus faculty:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Describe the proper care based on the most up-to-date scientific research.</li>\r\n	<li>Inappropriate variation in value-based approaches should be reduced</li>\r\n	<li>Give students more logical and sensible ways to approach the subject being taught.</li>\r\n	<li>increasing attention to lifelong learning</li>\r\n	<li>To draw attention to the flaws in the material already available and suggest relevant future research</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quality medical programmes are provided by SVDCH Chennai under the direction of highly qualified staff and cutting-ed