(101, 'JAIPUR DENTAL COLLEGE', NULL, 'jaipur-dental-college', '', NULL, 29, 629, '166391709334.jpg', '166391709330.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '6.8 Acres', '150', '2012', '', '', '<p><strong>JAIPUR DENTAL COLLEGE, JAIPUR</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of Jaipur&#39;s well-known private dental colleges is Jaipur Dental College. The college, also referred to as JDC Jaipur, was established in 2000&ndash;2001. One of the Best Private Dental Colleges in Jaipur has come to be associated with the institution. The Dental Council of India has given the college its approval and the college is associated with the Rajasthan University of Health Sciences (DCI).</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some top-notch programmes are provided by the JDC, which is run by highly qualified faculty members. Students can apply based on the courses they are enrolled in. The College is renowned for its five-year six months undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289118\"></a><a href=\"https://mymedicalcourse.com/course/bds\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>BDS</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Duration:&nbsp;<strong>4.6+1 years (4.6 years academics + 1 year internship)</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission through NEET.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fees&nbsp;for&nbsp;courses&nbsp;(Annual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; 13,20,000/-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Academic staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The faculty at this college is well-educated, well-trained, and equipped with contemporary technology. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are in charge of advancing and maintaining the standards of medical education at Jaipur Dental College Jaipur as faculty members.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>increase interns&#39; knowledge about dentistry.</li>\r\n	<li>Boost your clinical aptitude.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop self-assurance in one&#39;s abilities and skills. Boost your communication abilities.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop your professionalism.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop your research skills in science.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"JAIPUR DENTAL COLLEGE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"29\",\"city\":\"629\",\"degree\":\"BDS\\/MDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p>The following amenities are offered by JDC College which is mentioned below</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a name=\"_Hlk113288885\">Medical</a></li>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Sport</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n	<li>Centre of Community Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Social and Welfare Services.</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '', '<h2>Why Jaipur Dental College for BDS?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Established in the Year 2000</li>\r\n	<li>Best Private Dental College in North India<br />\r\n	Recognized by the Dental Council of India (DCI)</li>\r\n	<li>Recognized by Maharaj Vinayak Global University UGC</li>\r\n	<li>Tie-up with Implant Foundation, Germany</li>\r\n	<li>Well Established Department</li>\r\n	<li>Highly Experienced,</li>\r\n	<li>Skilled Faculty and Technicians</li>\r\n	<li>Modern Well equipped Laboratories</li>\r\n	<li>Separate Girls &amp; Boys Hostel with Mess</li>\r\n	<li>Transportation Services for the day scholars</li>\r\n	<li>111 Bed Maharaj Vinayak General Hospital &amp; Dental Clinics</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Dental Clinics</li>\r\n	<li>Seminars, Hands-on workshops, and Fellowship Programmes</li>\r\n	<li>CDE Programmes</li>\r\n	<li>Central Library</li>\r\n	<li>Professional &amp; Safe Campus Environment</li>\r\n	<li>Transparent Fee structure for all dental courses (BDS/MDS/Dental Diploma/ etc.</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '2022-09-13 16:11:30', '2022-09-23 12:11:33'),
(102, 'GEETANJALI DENTAL RESEARCH INSTITUTE', NULL, 'geetanjali-dental-research-institute', '', NULL, 29, 646, '166391749098.jpg', '166391749025.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30 Acres', '220', '2011', '13,20,000', '1500', '<p>One of the famous private dental colleges in Rajasthan is the Geetanjali Dental Research Institute in Udaipur. The college was established in 2014&ndash;15 and is also known as Geetanjali Dental Research Institute Udaipur. The Dental Council of India has recognised the institution, which is connected with Geetanjali University in Udaipur (DCI). To provide students with the greatest oral and maxillofacial surgery as well as dental treatment, Geetanjali Dental Research Institute in was founded.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some top-notch programmes are provided by the Geetanjali Dental Research Institute, which run by highly qualified faculty members. Students can apply based on the courses they are enrolled in. The College is renowned for its five-year six months undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289118\"></a><a href=\"https://mymedicalcourse.com/course/bds\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>BDS</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Duration:&nbsp;<strong>4.6+1 years (4.6 years academics + 1 years internship)</strong></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission through NEET.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fees&nbsp;for&nbsp;courses&nbsp;(Annual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; 13,20,000/-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Academic staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The faculty at this college is well-educated, well-trained, and equipped with contemporary technology. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for maintaining and enhancing the calibre of medical education at GDRI Udaipur as faculty members. The following policies, which are applicable, are followed by all campus faculty: encourage effective resource utilisation</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inappropriate variation in value-based approaches should be reduced</li>\r\n	<li>Give students more logical and sensible ways to approach the subject being taught.</li>\r\n	<li>increasing attention to lifelong learning</li>\r\n	<li>Describe the proper care based on the most up-to-date scientific research.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"GEETANJALI DENTAL RESEARCH INSTITUTE\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"29\",\"city\":\"646\",\"degree\":\"BDS\\/MDS\",\"exam\":\"Neet\"}', '<p><strong>Facilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a name=\"_Hlk113288885\">Medical</a></li>\r\n	<li>Computer Labs</li>\r\n	<li>Sport</li>\r\n	<li>Auditorium</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Blood Bank</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory</li>\r\n	<li>Hospital</li>\r\n	<li>OPD</li>\r\n	<li>Centre of Community Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Social and Welfare Services.</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', '', '', '2022-09-13 16:26:14', '2022-09-23 12:18:41'),
(103, 'EKLAVYA DENTAL COLLEGE & HOSPITAL', NULL, 'eklavya-dental-college--hospital', '', NULL, 29, 636, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30 Acres', '459', '1998', '2,75,000', '140', '<p>One of the reputable private dental colleges in Rajasthan is Eklavya Dental College &amp; Hospital Kotputli. The institution was established in 2005&ndash;2006 and is often known as Eklavya Dental College Kotputli. The Dental Council of India has given the college its approval and the college is associated with the Rajasthan University of Health Sciences (DCI).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To provide students with the greatest oral and maxillofacial surgery as well as dental treatment, Eklavya Dental College Kotputli was founded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some top-notch programmes are provided by the Eklavya Dental College &amp; Hospital Kotputli, which is run by highly qualified faculty members. Students can apply based on the courses they are enrolled in. The College is renowned for its five-year six month undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289118\"></a><a href=\"https://mymedicalcourse.com/course/bds\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>BDS</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Duration:&nbsp;<strong>4.6+1 years (4.6 years academics + 1 years internship)</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission through NEET.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fees&nbsp;for&nbsp;courses&nbsp;(Annual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; 2,75,000/-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Academic staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The faculty at this college is well-educated, well-trained, and equipped with contemporary technology. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for maintaining and raising the calibre of medical education at EDCH Kotputli as faculty members. The following policies, which are appli