(104, 'DARSHAN DENTAL COLLEGE AND HOSPITAL', NULL, 'darshan-dental-college-and-hospital', '', NULL, 29, 646, '166314800089.jpg', '1663148000100.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '30 Acres', '150', '1999', '2,00,000', '2500+', '<p>One of the well-known private dental colleges in Udaipur is Darshan Dental College &amp; Hospital. The institution was established in 1999&ndash;2000 and is often known as Darshan Dental College Udaipur. The Darshan Dental College was founded to meet the demand for highly trained dental surgeons in the following areas. Numerous labs and lecture halls have been built to meet and even exceed the standards set by the Dental Council of India and the University. To provide students with the best oral and maxillofacial surgery as well as dental treatment, Darshan Dental College &amp; Hospital Udaipur was established. College is affiliated with Rajasthan university of health and sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quality medical programmes are provided by DDCH under the direction of highly qualified faculty and cutting-edge facilities. The College is renowned for its five-year six months undergraduate medical programmes and three-year postgraduate medical programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a name=\"_Hlk113289118\"></a><a href=\"https://mymedicalcourse.com/course/bds\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>BDS</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Duration:&nbsp;<strong>4.6+1 years ( 4.6 years academics + 1 years internship )</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission through NEET.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fees&nbsp;for&nbsp;courses&nbsp;(Annual)&nbsp; -&nbsp; 2,00,000/-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Academic staff</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This college offers a solid mix of highly educated, well-trained, and tech-equipped faculty members. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for advancing and maintainin