(105, 'Vinayaka Mission\'s Sankarachariyar Dental College', NULL, 'vinayaka-missions-sankarachariyar-dental-college', '', NULL, 31, 725, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '30 Acres', '220', '1986', '4,10,000', '2500+', '<p><strong>Vinayaka Mission&#39;s Sankarachariyar Dental College, Salem, TN</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the top private dental colleges in Tamil Nadu is Vinayaka Mission&#39;s Sankarachariyar Dental College in Salem. The college was established in 1986&ndash;1987 and is commonly referred to as Vinayaka Mission Dental College Salem. The College has ties to Chennai&#39;s Tamil Nadu Dr. M.G.R. Medical University and has received the government of India&#39;s Dental Council approval. The College was founded to strengthen the nation&#39;s weakest region, the rural population. Sankarachariyar Dental College Salem was established by Vinayaka Mission to provide students with the best oral and maxillofacial surgery as well as dental care.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Faculty and Staff:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This college offers a solid mix of highly educated, well-trained, and technologically advanced faculty members. Additionally, there are enough non-technical staff members available to foster an environment where students can learn on their own. They are accountable for advancing and maintaining the standards of medical education at Vinayaka Mission Dental College Salem in their capacity as faculty members of the institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inappropriate variation in value-based approaches should be reduced</li>\r\n	<li>Give students more logical and sensible ways to approach the subject being taught.</li>\r\n	<li>Increasing attention to lifelong learning</li>\r\n	<li>To draw attention to the flaws in the material already available and suggest relevant future research</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courses Offered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The PDCH Pandur offers top-notch medical programmes with highly skilled faculty and cutting-edge facilities. For f