(114, 'Ramakrishna Ayurvedic Medical College', NULL, 'ramakrishna-ayurvedic-medical-college', '', NULL, 17, 362, '', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Ramakrishna Ayurvedic Medical College, Hospital &amp; Research centre was started in 1999.Institute is determined to impart training to students in basic principles &amp; philosophy of Ayurveda,integrating the modern scientific advances for providing better hospital care to the masses &amp; the society as a whole. Training involves advanced academics &amp; extracurricular activates to make them best physicians and responsible citizens The college is located within the city limits, 3 Kms from Yelahanaka railway station and Bus Stand,in serene atmosphere which is very conducive for studies. The campus has well stocked library ,reading room &amp;indoor auditorium. A herbal garden with more than 250 medicinal plant is available for demonstration. The College has a collection of over 200 wet specimens of rare plants in the pharmacology museum. The College has ample space for administrative office,class rooms, teaching and clinical departments, dissection theatre,labotory,museum,practical hall and student rest room. Department are spacious &amp; equipped with state of art modern teaching aids,laboroties ,museum and practical halls.Modren gadgetry lie ke OHP,LCD projects etc are used in the class rooms. Digital CCTV helps to oversee the activities in the college &amp; Hospital. Regular Yoga classes are conducted as part of curriculam.Aditionallly ,spoken English classes are arranged for the students to improve their communication skills and fluency in English.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Ramakrishna Ayurvedic Medical College\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"17\",\"city\":\"362\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Library and reading room</li>\r\n	<li>Herbal Garden &amp; Pharmacy</li>\r\n	<li>Tour/Seminar/Cultural activities</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel</li>\r\n	<li>Regular yoga classes are conducted as part of curriculum.</li>\r\n	<li>Additionally, spoken English classes are arranged for the students to improve their communication skills and fluency in English.</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', '', '', '2022-09-23 16:16:00', '2022-09-23 16:17:14'),
(115, 'Hillside Ayurvedic Medical College And Hospital', NULL, 'hillside-ayurvedic-medical-college-and-hospital', '', NULL, 17, 362, '166436183291.jpg', '166436183251.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '11 Arces', '150', '2014', '2100000', '2500+', '<p>Hillside Ayurveda Medical College and Hospital is one of the most prestigious colleges in the Ayurveda field. Ayurveda is one of the oldest schools of medicine in the world. Ayurveda is a healthcare system tuned with natural living. More than a medical system it is a way of life. The basic principles and medicines of Ayurveda found in the Hindu scriptures contain a series of prescriptions that can help humans overcome various ailments Ayurveda teaches one to live by nature following rules of nature in diet, exercise, and every part of being and doing. Ayurveda is an ancient Indian medical system. And has been developed by ancient sages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Hillside Ayurvedic Medical College And Hospital\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"17\",\"city\":\"362\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<p>Infrastructure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Class Rooms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cafeterias</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sports Facilities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Accommodation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transportation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Computer Centers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Laboratories</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Library</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2022-09-28 15:43:52', '2022-09-28 15:48:10'),
(116, 'Ashwini Ayurvedic Medical College & Research Centre', NULL, 'ashwini-ayurvedic-medical-college--research-centre', '', NULL, 17, 396, '166436310925.jpg', '166436310994.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>The Cradle To Health&quot; Ayurveda is known to be the most ancient method of natural healing of Indian origin. It is the traditional form of healing ailments in the body in the holistic way.<br />\r\nAshwini Ayurvedic Medical College and Research Centre has always taken the initiative to bring Ayurveda closer to people. This institution has its doors open for all.<br />\r\nAshwini Ayurvedic Medical College &amp; Research Centre was set up in the year 2004. Approved by AYUSH, Affiliated to Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Science, Bangalore.<br />\r\nThe institute is offering a comprehensive curriculum, professional training programs for the study of Authentic Ayurvedic Medicine and Surgery. Our Students are molded in such a way that, they become the healers of the future, successful Ayurvedic practitioners dedicated towards treating a person in Physical, Emotional and Spiritual way.<br />\r\nWe are dedicated to provide the highest quality education and health care in the field of Ayurveda.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Ashwini Ayurvedic Medical College & Research Centre\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Karnataka\",\"city\":\"Tumkur\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h2>Ambience:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ashwini Ayurvedic Medical College is situated in Tumkur District, which is 70 km from Bangalore, on the Bangalore &ndash; Honnavara Highway. The college is located a campus of 10 acres on the bank of the tank which has given it a serene atmosphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Class Room :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute provides well-equipped, very spacious, classrooms provided with advanced teaching aids, including Audio Visual Powerpoint presentation. The classroom provides an appropriate environment for students&#39; learning process and ensures audibility in each classroom with the Collar mike system.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Laboratory :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The College possesses a well equipped laboratory with all modern equipments and aides. The laboratory is open for the students in college hours under the observation of a lab technician.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Dissection Hall :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The dissection Hall is well lit and spacious, can accommodate 100 students.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pharmacy :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-equipped Rasa Shala is functioning to train students towards manufacturing medicinal preparations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Library :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The college has a well-equipped library with a good collection of books to cater to the needs of all students for collection, organization and dissemination of information. The latest edition of medical, para-medical and general books of famous authors are procured every year and offered for referencing and circulation. The library has got book section cum main reading hall with a reading capacity of 50 readers and a current journal section where latest journals are displayed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Herbal Garden :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Well-maintained, well irrigated herbal garden with a wide range of Ayurvedic herbs. Rare, endangered species are preserved with care. Herbs are utilized for study purpose and handpicked freshly for various Therapies.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Museum :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All departments are having excellent museum facilities for demonstration purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Auditorium :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-designed auditorium, capable of accommodating over 200 students at a time has been constructed, keeping all the needs of the students like conducting seminars, guest lecturers and other extra curricular activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Residential Facility :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Girls hostel situated in the college campus consists of well designed blocks and common dining hall food served both vegetarian &amp; Non-vegA well designed auditorium, capable of accommodating over 200 students at a time has been constructed, keeping all the needs of the students like conducting seminars, guest lecturers and other extracurricular activities.etarian in the campus. An efficient hygienic mess has been possible by dedicated staff and student representatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Canteen :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-maintained canteen is functioning to the needs of residents and Patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Security :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>24x7 securities for convenience, comfort and safety of Residents.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Clinical Facility :</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Students will receive clinical training at Ashwini Hospital. During the training period, students are assigned hospital duties for their clinical experience in various departments.</p>', '5', '', NULL, NULL, '2022-09-28 16:05:09', '2022-09-28 16:05:09'),
(117, 'Atreya Ayurvedic Medical College', NULL, 'atreya-ayurvedic-medical-college', '', NULL, 17, 374, '166436734532.jpg', '166436734517.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Atreya Ayurvedic Medical College actualises providing unprecedented medical training to produce successful Ayurvedic practitioners and researchers. Students graduate as proud alumni of one of the largest Ayurvedic institutions in the country.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The avidity of an eminent Ayurvedic practitioner, Dr. Prashant S Acharya, to inculcate a community with the real sense of health care through the great science of Ayurveda culminated in the establishment of a health care organisation in 2003 to serve the rural population confined to a small town, Dodaballapura, of the Bangalore district of Karnataka.</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Atreya Ayurvedic Medical College\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"17\",\"city\":\"374\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h3>Laboratories</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/labs.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Library</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/library.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Digital Access</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/internet.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Pharmacy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/pharma.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Museums</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/museum.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Hostel</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/hostel.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spacious and furnished hostel facilities are made available for the students, separate for boys and girls, with complete basic requirements, essential hygiene and healthy food.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Herbal Garden</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/garden.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Classrooms</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.atreyainstitution.com/images/classroom.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:900px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2022-09-28 17:15:45', '2022-09-28 17:24:18'),
(118, 'Prasanna College of Ayurveda and Hospital', NULL, 'prasanna-college-of-ayurveda-and-hospital', '', NULL, 17, 373, '166436998825.jpg', '166436998882.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'Affiliated', '', '30 Acres', '150', '2016', '15 Lacs', '2500+', '<p>Prasanna College of Ayurveda &amp; Hospital Belthangady&nbsp;is one of the reputed Private Ayurvedic Colleges in Belthangady. The college is popularly known as Prasanna College of Ayurveda, Prasanna Ayurvedic College Belthangady,&nbsp;founded in the year 2016. Prasanna College of Ayurveda &amp; Hospital started serving students with the best ayurvedic care. Prasanna Ayurvedic College Belthangady is affiliated With Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sciences, Bangalore, and approved by the&nbsp;Central Council of Indian Medicines (CCIM).</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Prasanna College of Ayurveda and Hospital\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"17\",\"city\":\"373\",\"degree\":\"BAMS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Well equipped with physical infrastructures like big classrooms, good and clean surroundings, ample water facility, play grounds, toilets, good library, transportation, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Separate and secure hostels for boys and girls.</li>\r\n	<li>Away from the disturbances and nuisances of the city.</li>\r\n	<li>Separate, well equipped laboratories alng with dissection hall.</li>\r\n	<li>Special coaching classes will be conducted for Examinations.</li>\r\n	<li>Individual attention.</li>\r\n	<li>Enthusiastic, dedicated and qualified lecturers for all subjects.</li>\r\n	<li>Encouragement for hardworking and intelligent students.</li>\r\n	<li>Students can utilize the college library for all subjects.</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious herb garden are present for better learning and training.</li>\r\n	<li>100 beds hospital with spacious and well ventilated Special, Semi special and general ward facilities</li>\r\n	<li>Quality Education is the aim of Prasanna Group of Institutions.</li>\r\n</ul>', '4.8', '', '', '', '2022-09-28 17:41:11', '2022-09-28 18:02:22'),
