(125, 'A.C.S Medical College & Hospital', NULL, 'acs-medical-college--hospital', '', 'india', 31, 693, '167687453146.jpg', '167687453188.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '1st Yr Fees', '₹ 4,740,000', '', '<p>The Faculty of Medical Sciences is an important department in the university and has a huge intake of students each year. The department comes fully equipped with a state-of-the-art laboratory, which makes it one of the best medical schools in Nigeria and other developing countries. The quality of education, infrastructural advantage and modern equipments are also some reasons why this university is very popular among students.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Undergraduate Program:-</h2>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:701px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff; vertical-align:top; width:307px\">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MBBS &ndash; Bachelor of Medicine Bachelor of Surgery</a></li>\r\n				<li>Postgraduate Program:-</li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Anatomy</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Biochemistry</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Community Medicine</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Dermatology Venereology Leprosy</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Forensic Medicine</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; General Medicine</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Microbiology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Pediatrics</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Pathology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Pharmacology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Physiology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Psychiatry</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MD &ndash; Radio Diagnosis</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MS &ndash; Obstetrics and Gynecology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MS &ndash; General Surgery</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MS &ndash; OtoRhinolaryngology</a></li>\r\n				<li><a href=\"https://acsmch.ac.in/?page_id=13#\">MS &ndash; Ophthalmology</a></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n\r\n			<p><strong>Course</strong></p>\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n\r\n			<p>M.B.B.S (Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Duration</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>4 Years 6 Months + 1 Year Internship</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Eligibility</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;Age limit: To be admitted to the Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery (M.B.B.S) Course the candidate should have completed 17 years on or before the 1st July in the academic year he / she is seeking admission.</p>\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n\r\n			<p><strong>Course</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>M.B.B.S (Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Duration</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>4 Years 6 Months + 1 Year Internship</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Eligibility</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;Age limit: To be admitted to the Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery (M.B.B.S) Course the candidate should have completed 17 years on or before the 1st July in the academic year he / she is seeking admission.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"A.C.S Medical College & Hospital\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '<p><strong>OP SERVICE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Spacious waiting hall, well-equipped examination chambers</li>\r\n	<li>Seperate rooms for special clinics like immunisation, baby clinic and family welfare clinic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IP SERVICE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The general ward has bed strength of 300 with the bed occupancy exceeding 85%</li>\r\n	<li>Children with diarrheal disease and infections are treated in separate cubicles.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The Central Laboratory functioning round-the-clock is the backbone of the medical services. The Departments of Biochemistry, Pathology and Clinical Microbiology are integrated into the Central Laboratory Services to provide rapid results to facilitate swift decision-making by consultants of all specialties.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>', '4.5', '', '', '', '2023-02-20 12:28:51', '2023-02-20 12:36:30'),
(126, 'SRI LAKSHMINARAYAN COLLEGE OF PHARMACY', NULL, 'sri-lakshminarayan-college-of-pharmacy', '', 'india', 31, 693, '167687699572.jpg', '167687699512.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '₹ 175,0001st Yr Fees', '', '<p>The Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences, Puducherry was born in the year 2006 with a vision to establish a multispecialty hospital where in particular poor could receive advanced care in an atmosphere of love and compassion. Annually 250 students admitted for undergraduate MBBS course, postgraduate degrees - Community Medicine, General Medicine, General Surgery and Radiology Otorhinolaryngology and Orthopaedics Dermatology Psychiatry Anaesthesiology Pediatrics Emergency Medicine Ophthalmology OBG Ph.D programmes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bachelor of Education (B.Ed)</strong><br />\r\nAnnual Intake : 100<br />\r\nCourse Duration : 2 Years<br />\r\nMajor : Tamil ,English, Mathematics ,Physical Science, Biological Science,Computer Science, History, Commerce</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B.Ed - Bachelor of Education</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Affiliated to Tamilnadu Teachers Education University</li>\r\n	<li>Recognized by Government of Tamilnadu</li>\r\n	<li>Recognized by National Council for Teacher Education (NCTE)</li>\r\n	<li>2 years Graduate Programme</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Admission Eligibility</strong><br />\r\nPass in any Degree examination of Tamilnadu University or any University in India or abroad, recognized as equivalent through 10+2+3 pattern of education with 45% of marks in aggregate to SC, ST,C1, Physically challenged candidates and 50% of marks in aggregate to other category.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Candidates who have been allotted through centralized counselling by the MCC of DGHS, New Delhi for admission to MBBS Degree courses in Sri Lakshmi Narayana Institute of Medical Sciences,Puducherry for the academic year 2022-23, are advised to report and complete the admission process strictly within the date and time specified in the <strong>&lsquo;Allotment Letter&rsquo;</strong> issued by the <a href=\"http://www.mcc.nic.in/\"><strong>MCC - DGHS.</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS to the UG candidates allotted through centralized counselling by MCC of DGHS, New Delhi for admission to MBBS Courses (2022-23)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Course</th>\r\n			<th>Fees</th>\r\n			<th>Eligibility</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>M.Pharm</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>₹1.5 Lakhs (1st Year Fees)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>B.Pharm.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>D.Pharma</td>\r\n			<td>₹67,000 (1st Year Fees)</td>\r\n			<td>10+2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>B.Pharma</td>\r\n			<td>₹1.32 Lakhs (1st Year Fees)</td>\r\n			<td>10+2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Pharm.D</td>\r\n			<td>₹2.07 Lakhs (1st Year Fees)</td>\r\n			<td>Post Graduation</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"SRI LAKSHMINARAYAN COLLEGE OF PHARMACY\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Tamil Nadu\",\"city\":\"Chennai\",\"degree\":\"\",\"exam\":\"\"}', '', '4.5', '', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-20 13:09:55', '2023-02-20 13:09:55'),
(127, 'Chettinad Academy of Research and Education', NULL, 'chettinad-academy-of-research-and-education-3', '', 'india', 31, 693, '167688177984.jpg', '167688177991.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', 'MCI', '', '6.8', '550', '', '', '2500+', '<p>CARE is the first university of its kind in Chennai which has been conferred with Deemed University. The academic programs offered by CARE are job oriented, innovative and professional. We offer 74 Academic programs in the Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Allied Health Sciences(AHS), Pharmacy, Physiotherapy, Architecture, Commerce and Law. Most of the programs offered are recognized by MCI/NMC/TNNMC/COA/BCI/PCI and other regulators.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The application window for the NEET PG 2023 exam which is to be held on 5th March, 2023 is closed now but the Final Edit Window to rectify any uploaded image such as Photograph, Signature or Thumb impression will be open from 14th to 17th February, 2023.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Application form for Counselling for MD MS admissions in Tamil Nadu:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The counselling for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu is conducted by the Directorate of Medical Education, Tamil Nadu (DME). The application form for PG admissions in Tamil Nadu has not been released yet and will be available online at the official website <a href=\"https://tnmedicalselection.net/\">Selection Committee- DME (tnmedicalselection.net)</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Under Graduate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 &frac12; year +1 year internship</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver11\">Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery (MBBS)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>POSTGRADUATE COURSES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M.D. Pre and Para Clinical (3 years)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver21\">M.D. (Anatomy)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver22\">M.D. (Physiology)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver23\">M.D. (Microbiology)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver24\">M.D. (Pharmacology)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver25\">M.D. (Pathology)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver26\">M.D. (Community Medicine)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver27\">M.D. (Biochemistry)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>POSTGRADUATE COURSES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M.D./M.S. Clinical Courses (3 years)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver31\">M.D. (General Medicine)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver32\">M.D. (Anesthesiology)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver33\">M.D. (Dermatology, Venerology and Leprosy)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver34\">M.D. (Respiratory Medicine)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver35\">M.D. (Paediatrics)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver36\">M.D. (Psychiatry)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver37\">M.D. (Radio-diagnosis)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://care.edu.in/school/faculty-of-medicine/faculty-of-medicine-admissions/#tabver38\">M.D. (Sports Medicine)</a></p>\r\n\r\