(128, 'BGS College Banglore', NULL, 'bgs-college-banglore', '', 'india', 17, 362, '167695964125.jpg', '', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Established by His Holiness Jagadguru Padmabushana Acharya Sri Gnanananda Tirtha Mahaswamiji, Sri Jayachamarajendra Swamiha and President Adichunchanagiri Shikshana in the year 1974. The BGS and SJB group of institutions is situated amidst tranquil environment with finest infrastructure. Each institute is accoutered with futuristic classrooms and neoteric laboratories to create a favorable environment for teaching, learning and patient care. The students acquire quality of education by instigating innovative and advanced methods through various avant-garde programs which facilitate not only in advancement of academics but life as well. The BGS and SJB group of institutions value in imparting comprehensive educational programme which enhances the vision and mission of the students.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Programme and Courses offered:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Under Graduate (UG) Programme in ENGINEERING &amp; TECHNOLOGY with &nbsp;Medical Sciences (NBEMS).For MD MS admissions in any college across Tamil Nadu, one needs to qualify the NEET PG examination which is the National Eligibility cum Entrance Test for Post Graduate courses in Medicine conducted by the National Board of Examinations in</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"BGS College Banglore\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Karnataka\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\\/MD\\/MS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2023-02-21 12:07:21', '2023-02-21 12:10:45'),
(129, 'Akash Group of Institutions, Bangalore', NULL, 'akash-group-of-institutions-bangalore', '', 'india', 17, 362, '167696101356.jpg', '167696101347.png', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Akash Group of Institutions is the leading educational institution having a foundation laid in 2014. A state of the art campus situated in Bangalore, The Silicon Valley of India. The institute has grown into one of the leading academic institutions in Karnataka</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Courses offered at Akash Institute of Medical Science &amp; Research Centre</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Akash Institute of Medical Science and Research Centre offers medical courses. The Akash Institute of Medical Science and Research Centre is approved by Medical Council of India (MCI) and is also approved by Government of India and Government of Karnataka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Courses offered in Akash Institute of Medical Science and Research Centre</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"Akash Group of Institutions, Bangalore\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Karnataka\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"degree\":\"MBBS\\/MD\\/MS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '<h3>Akash Hospital</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Akash Institute of Medical Science and Research Centre has its own Teaching Hospital with all the cutting-edge infrastructure and treatment facilities. The <a href=\"https://www.akashinstitutions.com/hospital\"><strong>Akash Hospital </strong></a>is developed according to the standard norms with Indian Medical Association (IMA) and Medical Council of India (MCI).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Akash Hospital is fully equipped with cutting edge medical technologies for top-notch treatment facilities and highly qualified doctors and specialists. The Akash hospital is equipped with 600 to 1000 beds and has a separate Pre-clinical, Para-clinical and Clinical Departments for the benefit of the patients. The <a href=\"https://www.akashinstitutions.com/hospital\"><strong>Akash Hospital</strong></a> played a key role during the Covid 19 pandemic by providing emergency response and treatments for the patients.</p>', '5', '', '', '', '2023-02-21 12:30:13', '2023-02-21 12:31:49'),
(130, 'East Point College of Medical Sciences', NULL, 'east-point-college-of-medical-sciences', '', 'india', 17, 362, '1677229593100.jpg', '167722959399.jpg', 'Private', 'Co-Ed', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p>East Point College of Medical Sciences and Research Centre, Bangalore is a unique institution offering multi-subject programs in technology and arts, sciences, humanities and health sciences. Educated by Dr S M Venkatpathi, it is guided by Mr Pramod Gowda who serves as its CEO. The campus harbours an array of institutions such as Engineering &amp; Technology, Management and Nursing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBBS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Master&rsquo;s Degree</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Paediatrics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Radio Diagnosis</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Pathology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Anaesthesiology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Dermatology , Venereology &amp; Leprosy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - General Medicine</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Pharmacology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MD - Social &amp; Preventive Medicine / Community Medicine</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MS - Ophthalmology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MS - Orthopaedics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MS - Obstetrics and Gynaecology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MS - Otorhinolaryngology</p>', 0, '', 1, '{\"name\":\"East Point College of Medical Sciences\",\"streams\":null,\"state\":\"Karnataka\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"degree\":\"MBBS,MD\\/MS\",\"exam\":\"NEET\"}', '', '5', '', '', '', '2023-02-24 15:06:33', '2023-02-24 15:17:45'),
