(7, 'Library Advisory Committee', '<p>Online based Library Advisory Committee meeting was conducted on 02.02.2022 at 02.30 PM. The committee members have attended the meeting with the...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online based Library Advisory Committee meeting was conducted on 02.02.2022 at 02.30 PM. The committee members have attended the meeting with the following agendas 1. Purchase of latest Edition Books for the year 2022, 2. Journal Subscription for the year 2022, 3. OPAC Computer to be placed, 4. Library OPAC to be linked with all department computers, 5. Library Membership card, 6. All department activities to be forwarded to Central Library for College Newsletter &quot;VMMC Pulse&quot; 7. Collecting Late fines and Xerox payment from students and staff via online payment portal like Gpay, Paytm</p>', 'library-advisory-committee', NULL, 1, 10, '2022-03-04 00:21:48', '2022-03-04 00:21:48'),
