(1, 8, '<p>Meenakshi Medical College Hospital And Research Institute student became massive success and practice in many top hospital around India. Check out our student placement details by clicking the download button.</p>', '2022-03-04 08:49:00', '2022-03-04 08:49:00'),
(2, 55, '<h3>Placement</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The placement cell plays a important function in finding task possibilities for beneath Graduates and submit Graduates passing out from the college by way of preserving in touch with reputed establishments. The placement cellular operates round the yr to facilitate contacts between faculties, schools and graduates. The range of students positioned through the campus interviews is continuously rising. On invitation, many institutions of recognition go to the college to behavior interviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We had been a hit in retaining our high placement facts through the years and the truth that our college students bear the recession blues with report breaking placements itself is an affidavit to our pleasant. Our creative alumnae have set new standards inside the company global through their estimable contributions and it&#39;s miles our company conviction that we are able to hold that legacy in the years yet to come.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Objective</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To motivate students to develop Technical knowledge and soft skills in terms of career planning and goal setting.</li>\r\n	<li>Personality Development Program.</li>\r\n	<li>Communication Skills Program.</li>\r\n	<li>Group Discussion Practice.</li>\r\n	<li>Mock Interview Sessions.</li>\r\n</ul>', '2022-03-10 17:15:37', '2022-03-10 17:15:37'),
(3, 44, '<p>INSIGHT</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>D.Pharma at ISF College of Pharmacy, Moga had the highest placement percentage of 100%</li>\r\n</ul>', '2022-03-12 11:46:10', '2022-03-12 11:46:10'),
(4, 61, '<p><strong>PLACEMENT CELL</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The placement cell of the college aims at providing guidance to the students about career opportunities&nbsp;and is engaged in conducting campus recruitments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>In- house Recruitment for</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bakson Homoeopathic Medical College &amp; Hospital&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bakson&#39;s&nbsp; Homoeopathic Centre for Allergy, Chain of Homoeopatic Clinics.</li>\r\n	<li>Bakson&#39;s Drugs &amp; Pharmaceuticals Private Limited</li>\r\n	<li>Liasoning is made with organizations, other than bakson Group , requiring Homoeopathic graduates/ Post graduate&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-03-15 14:25:52', '2022-03-15 14:25:52'),
(5, 74, '<h3><strong>&quot;Review of smvmch&quot;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Placement Experience&nbsp;:&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The college itself give 1 year coumplsory internship in our hospital with a payment. College also provide recuritment into different hospitals.</p>', '2022-07-19 19:15:02', '2022-07-19 19:15:02'),
(6, 115, '<p>In the past, Ayurveda doctors didn&rsquo;t have much options and had to start their own &lsquo;clinics&rsquo; after completing Ayruveday course. However, things have changed since then. As Ayurveda is gaining prominence in the country, ayurveda treatment is much sought after in the western coutnreis as well. As a result many Ayurveda Chikitisalayas, Ayurveda spas and retreats are coming up across the coutnry. Hence the prospect of Ayurveda is very promising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After successful completion of the course, students are placed in some of the most repuated Chikitsalayas or &ldquo;Ayurveda hospitals&rdquo; across the country. As a clinical practitioner, a student should be well-acquainted with different Ayurveda practices like Panchbhautik Chikitsa, Nadi Pariksha, Dhatu Chikitsa, etc. Depending upon their interests and expertise, students can choose a specialization and practice the tradition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternatively, students may also wish to pursue for higher studies and specialize in a particular field of Ayurveda which helps to get a better placement later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students who are not interested to pursue clinical practice, can be placed in management roles with different Ayurvedic hospitals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many ayurveda drug manufacturing companies also look for qualified ayruveda students. The job will be mostly in a factory setup. This is a promising career option and pays handsomely to the right candidate.</p>', '2022-09-28 15:51:46', '2022-09-28 15:51:46');
